(794, 365, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"bhdkhuf\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"fpaigcs\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"yrsqrdg\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Muri uyu muvugo ucuranze ukaba unahimbitse mu buryo bwa gihanga,Umusizi Tuyisenge aba yibaza byinshi ku myambarire n\'imitekerereze yo muri iyi minsi! Imwe mu mirongo igize uyu muvugo twavuga ni nkaho agera akibaza ati \\\"Ese Gihanga umuhanga ko yasize igihango,aho yagaruka agasanga ibyo yasize dusenga byarimukiye mu gusirimba,gusakuza biheruka burya? Ese yabikirwa ni iki? Na odeur ya ocean?cyangwa nawe batwikira ikoma bagashyira ku karubanda ubwambure bw\'umwami? Babikora nta dini batunga!\\\".<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Uyu n\'umwe mu mivugo uyu muhungu asa naho yakoze atishimiye uko imyambarire y\'ubu imeze. Muri uyu muvugo Umusizi Tuyisenge yumvikana anenga byeruye umuhanzikazi Odda Paccy usa nkaho ariwe wazanye iriya nkubiri yo kwambara ikoma.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Mu kiganiro ikinyamakuru Umuco wacu cyagiranye na Tuyisenge Olivier yatangiye agira ati \\\" Kwambara ubushwange aho ni umuco? cyangwa ni ubushwi bukuzwa bugakwirakwizwa? Ayo nayo n\'amwe mu magambo ari mu muvugo wanjye gusa icyo nifuza kuvuga n\'ukubwira abanyarwanda n\'abanyarwandakazi ko u Rwanda rugira umuco,kwambara amakoma ubundi ni igitutsi kibi,biriya si ibintu bikwiye umwali cyangwa umusore w\'i Rwanda, biba ngombwa ko umuntu akosora mugenzi nubwo ababikoze bose yenda ari bakuru kuri njye, ibuye ryahanuye inyoni bitangana.<\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p>\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0<img class=\\\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-366\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/TUYI-300x200.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"200\\\" \\/><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Umusizi akomeza atangariza Umuco wacu ko atakoze uyu muvugo mu rwego rwo kwibasira ababikoze kuko we ahamya ko ntan\'umwe baziranye byimbitse. Ikindi kandi akomeza asaba urubyiruko kutiruka inyuma y\'ibiguruka byose.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Uyu muvugo ukaba warakozwe n\'umuryango Iwacu in Africa biciye muri situdiyo Rwanda image Films. Iwacu in Africa ni umuryango wamaze gusinyisha abasizi icyenda b\'abanyarwanda mu rwego rwo kubafasha mu iterambere ry\'ibihangano byabo. Umusizi Tuyisenge aratangaza ko bidatinze n\'amashusho y\'uyu muvugo azaba kuba ugeze hanze.<\\/p><p>KANDA HANO\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/youtu.be\\/uaMkjwV8Ayo\\\">https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=uaMkjwV8Ayo<\\/a><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
