(841, 380, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"ajloviu\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"xqdendk\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"hzrjoyx\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Iki gitaramo cyo kumurika Alubumu Afro kizasusurutswa na Mani Martin ubwe afatanyije n\'abandi bahanzi bakomeye hano mu Rwanda. Bamwe mu bahanzi bazafatanya na Mani Martin aha twavuga nk\'Itorero Inkindi Itatse rizasurutsa abazitabira igitaramo Afro biciye mu nganzo gakondo yo kubyina no kuririmba kinyarwanda,iri torero ni naryo ryakoranye na Mani Martin mu ndirimbo Afro Remix ari nayo yitiriwe iyi alubumu, Azakorana kandi na Kesho Band muri muzika yumwimerere[Live Music].<\\/p><p>Iki gitaramo kizitabirwa kandi n\'abandi bahanzi banyuranye nka Yverry umwe mu bahanzi b\'abahanga akaba yaranarangije mu ishuri ry\'umuziki ku Nyundo.<\\/p>[caption id=\\\"attachment_381\\\" align=\\\"alignnone\\\" width=\\\"225\\\"]<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-381\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/download.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"225\\\" height=\\\"225\\\" \\/> Yverry[\\/caption]<p>Undi uzitabira iki gitaramo ni Sinitex umwe mu bahanzi bari gukora cyane muri iyi minsi ndetse akaba ari na mukuru w\'umunyamakuru akaba n\'umunyarwenya Nkusi Arthur.<\\/p>[caption id=\\\"attachment_382\\\" align=\\\"alignnone\\\" width=\\\"300\\\"]<img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-382\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/DURHDrx-300x215.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"215\\\" \\/> SINTEX[\\/caption]<p>Undi uzaririmba muri Afro ni Muneza Christophe(Christopher) umwe mu bahanzi b\'abahanga\\u00a0\\u00a0mu njyana ya R&amp;B.<\\/p>[caption id=\\\"attachment_383\\\" align=\\\"alignnone\\\" width=\\\"300\\\"]<img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-383\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/Rdg9UEk-300x268.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"268\\\" \\/> Muneza Christophe(Christopher)[\\/caption]<p>Afro Izitabirwa kandi n\'itsinda Yemba Voice bamwe mu bahanzi b\'abahanga nabo bakaba bari mu banyeshuri bize ku ishuri rya muzika ku Nyundo.<\\/p>[caption id=\\\"attachment_384\\\" align=\\\"alignnone\\\" width=\\\"300\\\"]<img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-384\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/yYmTS9O-300x169.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"169\\\" \\/> Yemba Voice[\\/caption]<p>Mu kiganiro ikinyamakuru Umuco wacu cyagiranye na Mani Martin yatangiye agira ati\\\" Imyiteguro y\'igitaramo cyo kumurika alubumu yanjye irakataje, icyo nabwira abanyarwanda n\'ukwitabira ku bwinshi iki gitaramo kuko kiri muri bimwe mu bitaramo bihendutse kandi bizaba birimo ubuhanga\\\".<\\/p><p>Mani Martin abajijwe uburyo azakorana n\'Itorero Inkindi Itatse yasubije agira ati \\\" Uko tuzakorana ni agaseke gapfundikiye bizabonwa nuzahagera niyo mpamvu mbararikiye kuzahagera\\\".<\\/p><p>Umuyobozi w\'itorero Inkindi Itatse abajijwe uko itorero ayoboye ryiteguye gususurutsa abazitabira igitaramo Afro yabwiye ikinyamakuru Umuco wacu ati \\\"Imyiteguro ku ruhande rw\'Inkindi Itatse imyiteguro irarimbanyije rwose kugira ngo tuzashimishe abanyarwanda n\'abanyamahanga bazitabira igitaramo cyo kumurika alubumu Afro\\\".<\\/p>[caption id=\\\"attachment_388\\\" align=\\\"alignnone\\\" width=\\\"300\\\"]<img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-388\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/IMG-20171103-WA0012-300x200.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"200\\\" \\/> Inkindi Itatse[\\/caption][caption id=\\\"attachment_386\\\" align=\\\"alignnone\\\" width=\\\"300\\\"]<img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-386\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/I9jIag7-300x175.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"175\\\" \\/> Kesho Band na Mani Martin[\\/caption]<p>Igitaramo cyo kumurika alubumu Afro ya Mani Martin kizaba kuri uyu wa gatandatu tariki ya 04\\/Ugushyingo\\/2017 muri Kigali Serena Hotel guhera i saa moya z\'umugoroba kwinjira ni ibihumbi bitanu(5000Rwf) ahasanzwe ndetse ni ibihumbi icumi(10000Rwf) mu cyubahiro.<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-387\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/IMG-20171103-WA0010-300x300.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"300\\\" \\/><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
