(921, 419, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"kbmtmgd\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"sugqcjh\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"qghlave\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><b><strong>Poetic fever ni igitaramo ngaruka kwezi,gitegurwa na Transpoesis. Igitaramo Poetic Fever cy\'uku kwezi k\'Ukwakira kikazaba ku wa 14\\/Ukwakira\\/2017 muri Blue Note mu mujyi hafi ya Ecole Belge.<\\/strong><\\/b><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Transpoesis ni umuryango uharanira impinduka binyuze mu busizi,uyu muryango ukaba warashinzwe mu mwaka wa 2015, ushingwa n\'umuzungukazi ukomoka mu gihugu cy\'Ubusuwisi Dr Andrea Grieder.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Transpoesis itegura ibitaramo ndetse n\'amahugurwa anyuranye ku busizi, uretse amarushanwa yitwa Kigali Itatswe n\'Ubusizi,uyu muryango mu kwezi gushize kwa Nzeri watangiye gutegura ikindi gitaramo cy\'ubusizi\\u00a0\\u00a0aricyo cyitwa \\\"Poetic Fever\\\",iki gitaramo gihuza abasizi batandukanye bakomeye Transpoesis iba yahisemo hanyuma bagataramira abantu.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Iki gitaramo kiba gifite umwihariko wuko abasizi batarama bacurangirwa n\'itsinda ry\'abacuranzi(Band) ryitwa Kinga Blues riyoborwa n\'umunyamuziki kabuhariwe ukomoka mu gihugu cy\'Uburundi Arnauld Nganji.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Poetic Fever y\'uku kwezi ku ukwakira izitabirwa n\' ibyamamare mu Busizi hano mu Rwanda ndetse no mu karere k\'Afurika y\'uburasirazuba.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Bamwe mu basizi bazitabira iki gitaramo navuga Maniraguha Carine,uyu ni umukobwa ugaragaza ubuhanga mu busizi bwo mu rurimi rw\' Ikinyarwanda akaba n\'umwe mu begukanye irushanwa Kigali Itatswe n\'Ubusizi.\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0<\\/p>[caption id=\\\"attachment_306\\\" align=\\\"alignnone\\\" width=\\\"300\\\"]<img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-306\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/10\\/cBmQdF2-300x200.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"200\\\" \\/> Maniraguha Carine[\\/caption]<p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0Mu bandi basizi bazasusurutsa abazitabira Poetic Fever harimo Fefe Karume umuhanga mu busizi mu rurimi rw\'Igifaransa, Sam Ruhindi(ISamiejr) umwe mu basizi b\'abahanga kandi bafite umwihariko mu busizi mu rurimi rw\'icyongereza, Akeem Marvin nawe n\'umwe muri bakabuhariwe mu busizi bw\'Icyongereza,atondeka imirongo ugatwarwa ukananirwa kwihishira ukabigaragaza.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/p>[caption id=\\\"attachment_417\\\" align=\\\"alignnone\\\" width=\\\"300\\\"]<img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-417\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/IMG-20171009-WA0009-300x225.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"225\\\" \\/> Fefe Karume[\\/caption]<p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0<\\/p>[caption id=\\\"attachment_305\\\" align=\\\"alignnone\\\" width=\\\"300\\\"]<img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-305\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/10\\/fkbmbWV-300x200.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"200\\\" \\/> Sam Ruhindi(ISamiejr)[\\/caption]<p><img class=\\\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-418\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/IMG-20171009-WA0002-300x298.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"298\\\" \\/><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Akeem Marvin\\u00a0 icyirango cy\'umuvugo yise ibaruwa kuri perezida wanjye yatuye Perezida Kagame<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Iki gitaramo kizitabirwa na kabuhariwe mu busizi ukomoka mu gihugu cya Kenya witwa Eric Onyango Otieno uzwi ku izina rya Rix Poet iwabo mu gihugu cya Kenya<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-307\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/10\\/3QeA3Jm-300x200.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"200\\\" \\/><\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Iki gitaramo kizaba ku wa gatandatu tariki 14\\/Ukwakira\\/2017 guhera i saa moya n\'igice z\'umugoroba(7:30pm) mu mujyi iruhande rwa Ecole Belge ahitwa Blue Note hanyuma kwinjira ni ibihumbi bitatu by\'amafaranga y\'u Rwanda(3000rwf) ku basanzwe ndetse n\'igihumbi(1000rwf) ku banyeshuri bafite ikarita y\'ishuri<\\/span><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
