(946, 139, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"vemaeyo\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"wzabksq\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"opgaijf\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><b><strong>Makadeem ni umuhanzi gakondo ukomoka mu gihugu cya Kenya,akaba yaramenyekanye kubera gucuranga igicurangisho gakondo cy\'abanyakenya kitwa Nyatiti. Uretse kuba uyu muhanzi acuranga igicurangisho cya Nyatiti ni umucuranzi w\'ibindi bicurangisho byinshi bya muzika aribyo Guitar,Kalimba...<\\/strong><\\/b><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Makadeem abajijwe inkomoko y\'igicurangisho cya Nyatiti yatangiye ambwira ikinyamakuru umuco wacu ati \\\" Nyatiti ni igicurangisho gakondo gifite inkomoko mu gihugu cya Kenya by\'umwihariko mu bwoko bwa Luwo, mu bwoko bwa Luwo buri gicurangisho kigira umumaro wacyo,Nyatiti rero yo mu bwoko bwa Luwo ikunda gukoreshwa mu njyana zo kubyina.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Makadeem kandi yatangaje ko ari ubwa mbere yari ageze mu Rwanda avuga ko icyamutangaje akigera mu Rwanda ari isuku itangaje yagiye abona mu mujyi wa Kigali.<\\/p>[caption id=\\\"attachment_428\\\" align=\\\"alignnone\\\" width=\\\"300\\\"]<img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-428\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/0AodYOk-300x200.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"200\\\" \\/> Makadeem[\\/caption]<p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Makadeem abajijwe niba hari abahanzi b\'abanyarwanda azi yasubije agira ati\\\" Abahanzi b\'abanyarwanda turaziranye usibye ko atari benshi, muri abo navuga nka Deo Munyakazi, umuraperi witwa Prime,Angel Mutoni ndetse na Makonikoshwa turaziranye cyane\\\"<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Abajijwe icyo avuga ku nanga nk\'igicurangisho gakondo cy\'abanyarwanda ahamya ko gifite umwihariko yasubije agira ati\\\" Ubundi numva inanga bwa mbere ndatekereza byari muri Werurwe uyu mwaka iwacu mu gihugu cya Kenya ubwo numvaga Munyakazi Deo ayicuranga mu iserukiramuco ryitwa Ongea, numvise ifite uburyo ivuga bwihariye numva ndayikunze.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Abajijwe uko yabonye umuziki w\'abanyarwanda mu gihe gito yamaze mu Rwanda yasubije agira ati \\\" U Rwanda rufite umuziki mwiza, bwa mbere ngera ino natangiye kujya numva indirimbo za kera zicuranze mu nanga numva ndazikunze cyane,ndatekereza ko igihe kimwe nanjye nazakora indirimbo byibura yiganjemo umuco gakondo w\'abanyarwanda.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Uyu muhanzi kandi aherutse mu Rwanda mu byumweru bibiri bishize aho yari yakoranye igitaramo na bamwe mu bahanzi b\'abanyarwanda aha navuga nka Deo Munyakazi,Moise... iki gitaramo cyari cyabereye Roots house ku Kacyiru.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Makadeem yari yazanywe mu Rwanda n\'itsinda Afrogroov riyoborwa na Karengera Kirenga Eric Soul umuhungu wa Cecile Kayirebwa. Iri tsinda risanzwe ritegura ibitaramo gakondo rikanatumira bamwe mu bahanzi b\'ibyamamare ku migabane itandukanye y\'Isi. Mu bandi bahanzi iri tsinda ryazanye mu Rwanda twavuga nka Joss Stone umuririmbyikazi w\'umunyamerika akaba n\'umwe mu bafite kimwe mu bihembo bikomeye muri icyo gihugu aricyo Grammy award.<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Uyu muhanzi Makadeem amaze kumenyekana mu bihugu byinshi bitandukanye ku isi kuko amaze kuzenguruka imigabane myinshi acuranga iki gicurangisho cya Nyatiti!! Bimwe mu bihugu Makadeem amaze gucurangiramo Nyatiti ni nka Poland,Crossia,Mexico,Ubudage. Uyu muhanzi abajijwe ku bavuga ko umuziki wa Kenya waba warateye imbere mu buryo bwa kinyamwuga kurusha uw\'abanyarwanda yasubije yisekera ati\\\" Burya iyo umuhanzi akora kandi akagira abamukurikira(followers)sinzi aho umuntu yahera avuga ngo si umunyamwuga, ahubwo uwo waba uhakana ibyo akora numva we yakora ibye akamurusha. Ibyo rero byuko Kenya ari abanyamwuga kurusha abanyarwanda simbizi.\\\"<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Makadeem ni umwe mu bahanzi gakondo baba nyafurika bamaze gutumirwa n\'ibinyamakuru bikomeye hano ku isi aha navuga nka BBC,NBC,.. Makadeem aratangaza kandi agiye gukora uko ashoboye isi yose ikamenya Nyatiti!<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]');
