(937, 117, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"pxmbmei\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"vphhmie\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"tbqngfe\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><b>Abagize itsinda ComponentsRw rigizwe n\' umuvangavangamiziki(Dj) Karengera Kirenga Eric Soul, umukirigitananga Munyakazi Deo, abaraperi babiri aribo Mazimpaka Prime na Angel Mutoni, guhera kuri uyu wa 22 Nzeri 2017 barabarizwa mu murwa mukuru w\'igihugu cy\'Ubugande Kampala aho bitabiriye iserukiramuco ryitwa Bayimba Festival.<\\/b><\\/p><div align=\\\"left\\\">itsinda\\u00a0 ComponentsRw bahagurutse i Kigali mu gitondo cyo<br \\/> kuri uyu wa Gatanu berekeza mu gihugu cya Uganda ahagiye kubera iri<br \\/> serukiramuco rya Bayimba Festival rigiye kuba ku ncuro ya cumi, rikaba<br \\/> ryitabiriwe n\'abahanzi baturutse mu bihugu bitandukanye ku isi. Iri<br \\/> tsinda rihagarariye u Rwanda biteganyijwe ko riri bususurutse<br \\/> abitabiriye iri serukiramuco uyu munsi tariki ya 23\\/ Nzeri 2017 guhera<br \\/> i saa tatu z\'ijoro ku isaha yo mu bugande n\'ukuvuga saa mbili z\'ijoro<br \\/> ku isaha yo mu Rwanda.<p>Aba bahanzi baratangaza ko nyuma yo kugera Uganda amahoro bameze neza<br \\/> ko biteguye kuza gutarama bagacyura inganji nkuko Munyakazi Deo umwe<br \\/> mu bahanzi bagize itsinda ComponentsRw yabitangarije ikinyamakuru<br \\/> umucowacu.com Yatangiye agira ati \\\"Mukuri turiteguye cyane,twagerageje<br \\/> gukora imyitozo ihagije pee!! Ndagira ngo niba hari abanyarwanda bari<br \\/> inaha bakunda umuziki w\'umwimerere bazi kuza badushyigikire twe nka<br \\/> ComponentsRw duhagaze bwuma\\\".<\\/p><\\/div><div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><div align=\\\"left\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i.imgur.com\\/iynUhcb.jpg\\\" width=\\\"388\\\" height=\\\"388\\\" \\/><\\/div><div align=\\\"left\\\"><p>\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 MUNYAKAZI DEO<\\/p><div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i.imgur.com\\/lg6gvIB.jpg\\\" width=\\\"364\\\" height=\\\"260\\\" \\/><\\/p><\\/div><div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 (DJ) KARENGERA KIRENGA\\u00a0 ERIC SOUL<\\/div><div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><div align=\\\"left\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i.imgur.com\\/cwYrpHy.jpg\\\" width=\\\"385\\\" height=\\\"256\\\" \\/><\\/div><div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0\\u00a0 MUTONI ANGEL<\\/div><div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0<img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i.imgur.com\\/tiUsbCH.jpg\\\" width=\\\"326\\\" height=\\\"217\\\" \\/><\\/div><div align=\\\"left\\\">MAZIMPAKA\\u00a0 PRIME<\\/div><div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><div align=\\\"left\\\">Iri serukiramuco uretse itsinda rya ComponentsRw ryaryitabiriye,<br \\/> ryitabiriwe kandi nabandi bahanzi<br \\/> bakomeye barimo itsinda rya Umoja Boys ryo mu<br \\/> Buholandi,Slyvester &amp; Abramz, bo muri Uganda,<br \\/> Maurice Kirya ,Makadem wo muri Kenya, Coopy<br \\/> Bly, Cindy Sanyu, Berita wo muri Afurika y\\u2019Epfo,<br \\/> Feridah Rose, Jose Chameleone ,Bobi Wine,ndetse nabandi benshi batandukanye.<p>Iri tsinda rya ComponentsRw ryaherukaga mu gihugu cya Uganda muri<br \\/> Gicurasi mu iserukiramuco ryiswe Doadoa Festival, iri tsinda kandi<br \\/> ryanitabiriye umuhuro w\'abahanzi bo muri Afurika witwa Ongea wabereye<br \\/> muri Kenya mu kwezi kwa Werurwe uyu mwaka.<\\/p><\\/div>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
