(1055, 82, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"ebaacsv\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"zfknfty\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"njumbyf\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><b>Abaturage babarirwa mu bihumbi bahuriye mu birori byo kwizihiza umunsi w\\u2019Umuganura byaranzwe n\\u2019ibyishimo bisangiwe hagati yabo n\\u2019ababayobora<\\/b><\\/p><div align=\\\"left\\\"><div><br \\/>Ibi birori by\\u2019Umuganura byizihizwaga mu Rwanda rwo hambere bigahuza abishimira umusaruro n\\u2019ibyejejwe, kuri iyi nshuro byabereye mu Karere ka Nyanza.<br \\/><p>Mu ijambo rye, Minisitiri w\\u2019Umuco na Siporo, Uwacu Julienne, yavuze ko kwizihiza Umuganura ku rwego rw\\u2019umuryango, ari umwanya wo gushimangira ubumwe bw\\u2019abawugize no gusabana ariko by\\u2019akarusho uw\\u2019uyu mwaka ukaba ubaye mu gihe Abanyarwanda bakishimira intsinzi ya Perezida wa Repubulika, Paul Kagame.<\\/p><p>Yagize ati \\\"Umuganura ni umunsi ukomeye ku Banyarwanda kubera agaciro kawo, ni umwanya wo kwishimira ibyo tumaze kugeraho mu iterambere ry\\u2019igihugu cyacu. Ni umwanya wo kwisuzuma tukareba ibitaragenze neza no guhigira imyaka ije, ni n\\u2019umwanya wo gusabana kw\\u2019abayobozi n\\u2019abayoborwa. Muri iki gihe, tuganura twishimira umusaruro tugezeho mu nzego zose z\\u2019ubuzima bw\\u2019igihugu.\\\"<\\/p><br \\/><br \\/><br \\/><br \\/><div><img class=\\\"artimgv5 img-responsive\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L1000xH667\\/umuganura_11-aee7c.jpg?1503865178\\\" width=\\\"282\\\" height=\\\"188\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" \\/><\\/div><br \\/><br \\/><br \\/><br \\/><br \\/><\\/div>Yongeyeho ati \\u201cUmuganura ugomba kongera kutwibutsa ko umuryango ari wo shingiro ry\\u2019imbaraga z\\u2019Abanyarwanda, uje mu gihe tukishimira ibyo<\\/div><div align=\\\"left\\\">u Rwanda rumaze kugeraho nyuma y\\u2019imyaka 23. Ni uwa mbere twizihije muri manda nshya y\\u2019imyaka irindwi ya Perezida wa Repubulika, Paul Kagame. Ubaye mu gihe tukizihiza intsinzi Abanyarwanda twagaragarije mu matora aherutse.\\u201d<\\/div><p align=\\\"left\\\">Yasoje avuga ko ashimangira agaciro Umuco Nyarwanda ufitiye abanyagihugu nk\\u2019uko ku munsi wari wabanje bongeye kwiyibutsa ubukungahare bwawo mu gitaramo \\u2018I Nyanza Twataramye\\u2019 cyaranzwe n\\u2019ibyishimo by\\u2019ikirenga ku bacyitabiriye bakabikomereza mu kwizihiza Umuganura.<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Nyuma y\\u2019Ijambo rya Minisitiri Uwacu hakurikiyeho umuhango wo kumurika Inyambo no kwinikiza ndetse n\\u2019uwo guha abana amata. Abitabiriye iki gikorwa bakoze ubusabane basangira ibigori n\\u2019indi myaka yejejwe mu Karere ka Nyanza kakiriye uyu muhango.<\\/p><div align=\\\"left\\\"><img class=\\\"artimgv5 img-responsive\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L1000xH667\\/36008438684_8b245d0ce8_k-955d7.jpg?1503856316\\\" width=\\\"317\\\" height=\\\"212\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" \\/><br \\/>Minisitiri w\\u2019Uburinganire n\\u2019Iterambere ry\\u2019Umuryango, Esp\\u00e9rance Nyirasafari aha abana amata mu muhango w\'Umuganura<div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><img class=\\\"artimgv5 img-responsive\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L1000xH768\\/36033676953_f98d217e94_k-3e172.jpg?1503856316\\\" width=\\\"281\\\" height=\\\"215\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" \\/><br \\/>Minisitiri wa Siporo n\\u2019Umuco, Uwacu Julienne aha abana amata<div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><\\/div><p align=\\\"left\\\">Umuhango wo kwizihiza Umuganura wanabereyemo igikorwa cyo kuremera abatishoboye aho abaturage bagera kuri 400 bahawe ubwisungane mu kwivuza ndetse hakanatangwa inka 12. Bamwe mu baturage biteje imbere batanze ubuhamya bw\\u2019uko babigezeho mu gufatanya ndetse bagateza imbere na bagenzi babo mu gutanga imirimo.<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Ibi birori byasusurukijwe n\\u2019Itorero Urukerereza ryasusurukije imbaga mu mbyino zishimangira ubumwe, ubusabane ndetse zishimangira indangagaciro z\\u2019Umuco Nyarwanda. Byanaririmbwemo n\\u2019Indatabigwi, abanyeshuri bize umuziki ku Nyundo n\\u2019abahanzi batandukanye bakomeye barimo Riderman, Charly &amp; Nina, Rafiki, Ama G The Black n\\u2019abandi.<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Umunsi w\\u2019Umuganura kandi wanizihirijwe mu bice bitandukanye by\\u2019igihugu ku rwego rw\\u2019umudugudu.<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\"><strong>Ibyo wamenya ku birori by\\u2019Umuganura byizihizwa buri mwaka<\\/strong><\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Mu mateka y\\u2019u Rwanda, Umuganura wari umunsi mukuru ngarukamwaka wubahwaga kandi ugahabwa agaciro mu muryango w\\u2019Abanyarwanda. Watangiye kwizihizwa ahagana mu kinyejana cya cyenda, uza kongera guhabwa imbaraga n\\u2019Umwami Ruganzu II Ndoli (1510-1543) ubwo yabohoraga u Rwanda nyuma y\\u2019imyaka irenga 10 ruri mu maboko y\\u2019abanyamahanga (Abanyabungo).<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Umuganura wizihizwaga mu buryo bubiri, ku rwego rw\\u2019Igihugu wayoborwaga n\\u2019Umwami afashijwe n\\u2019abanyamihango bawo. Imihango y\\u2019ibwami yari iyo guhuza Imana n\\u2019Igihugu, bagahuza ibikorwa by\\u2019idini n\\u2019imigenzo gakondo hamwe n\\u2019imirimo y\\u2019ubuhinzi n\\u2019ubworozi. Ku rwego rw\\u2019umuryango, wayoborwaga n\\u2019umukuru wawo.<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Mu miryango abana basabanaga n\\u2019ababyeyi, hakabaho kwishimira ibyagezweho cyane cyane mu musaruro. Mu wa 1925, kwizihiza Umuganura byaciwe n\\u2019abakoloni, umwiru mukuru mu bawuyoboraga, Gashamura ka Rukangirashyamba aciribwa mu Burundi. Nyuma y\\u2019uko u Rwanda rubonye ubwigenge, abantu bakomeje kwizihiza Umuganura mu miryango yabo.<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Kwizihiza Umuganura muri iki gihe byarenze imbibi zo kwita ku musaruro w\\u2019ubuhinzi n\\u2019ubworozi gusa, bigera no mu zindi nzego zireba ubuzima n\\u2019iterambere by\\u2019Abanyarwanda hagamijwe kugaragaza urugendo Abanyarwanda barimo baharanira kwigira no kwibohora nyako bifashisha umuco wabo.<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Umuganura w\\u2019ubu wizihizwa hishimirwa umusaruro wagezweho mu nzego zitandukanye zirimo ubuzima, uburezi, ikoranabuhanga, imikino n\\u2019imyidagaduro, ubucuruzi, ubucukuzi bw\\u2019amabuye y\\u2019agaciro, ibikorwaremezo, inganda ndangamuco, ubukerarugendo n\\u2019ibindi. Usibye kwishimira ibyagezweho hanafatwa ingamba zo kugera ku mihigo itandukanye iba yaratekerejwe muri buri rwego.<\\/p><div align=\\\"left\\\"><img class=\\\"artimgv5 img-responsive\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L1000xH667\\/36033695293_fb598592be_k-1f42a.jpg?1503856316\\\" width=\\\"308\\\" height=\\\"228\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" \\/><div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><img class=\\\"artimgv5 img-responsive\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L1000xH667\\/abejeje_urutoki_n_indi_myaka_bagaragarije_abayobozi_ibyo_bagezeho-eaf9d.jpg?1503856316\\\" width=\\\"325\\\" height=\\\"217\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" \\/><br \\/>Abejeje urutoki bagaragarije ubuyobozi ibyo bagezeho<div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><img class=\\\"artimgv5 img-responsive\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L1000xH667\\/36033657493_a00e9f062d_k-d531c.jpg?1503856316\\\" width=\\\"374\\\" height=\\\"249\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" \\/><div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><img class=\\\"artimgv5 img-responsive\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L1000xH667\\/umuganura_10-9f595.jpg?1503865178\\\" width=\\\"384\\\" height=\\\"256\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" \\/><div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><img class=\\\"artimgv5 img-responsive\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L1000xH667\\/umuganura_23-63a5e.jpg?1503865178\\\" width=\\\"339\\\" height=\\\"226\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" \\/><div align=\\\"left\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><img class=\\\"artimgv5 img-responsive\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\