(1202, 85, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"teyovtm\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"bfslvnd\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"badbrzz\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p align=\\\"left\\\">Uru rutare rwitiriwe umugabo witwaga Kamegeri, akaba yararuboneyeho akaga yashakaga kugushamo abandi, bihita biba aka ya mvugo y\\u2019umugani nyarwanda bagira bati: \\\"<i>Urucira mukaso rugatwara nyoko\\\".<\\/i>Hari ibitabo bimwe bigaruka kuri aya mateka, aho usanga bamwita \\\"Kagemeri\\\" ariko izina nyaryo ni Kamegeri.<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Kamegeri\\u00a0uyu yari umutware ku ngoma y\\u2019umwami Mibambwe II Sekarongoro II Gisanura, ahagana mu mwaka w\\u20191672. Kamegeri yitiriwe uru rutare, nyuma y\\u2019uko barumutwikiyeho, ibyo bikaba byarabayeho ku itegeko ry\\u2019umwami Mibambwe II Sekarongoro II Gisanura, ibi akaba yarabyifuje nyuma y\\u2019aho Kamegeri yari yabwiye umwami ko abazajya bagira nabi bazajya barujugunywaho rumaze gucanirwa.<\\/p><div align=\\\"left\\\"><div><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/IMG\\/jpg\\/urutare_rwa_kamegeri.jpg\\\" width=\\\"480\\\" height=\\\"570\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" \\/><\\/div><dl class=\\\"spip_document_2972 spip_documents spip_documents_center\\\"><dt><\\/dt><\\/dl><\\/div><p align=\\\"left\\\">Uyu mwami Mibambwe II Sekarongoro II Gisanura, yari azwiho ubwitonzi, kugira ubuntu, guha amata abakene begereye ibwami no kwanga akarengane. Ibyo byatumye bamuhimba igisingizo bamwita\\u00a0<strong>\\u201cRugabishabirenge\\u201d<\\/strong>\\u00a0kuko yatangaga atitangiye itama. Yari azwiho kandi kuba umucamanza utabera kandi wangaga ko hatangwa ibihano bidakwiye umuntu.<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Umunsi umwe, Mibambwe II Sekarongoro II Gisanura, yabajije abatware be igihano gisumba ibindi bumva umuntu mubi cyane mu gihugu yajya ahabwa , buri wese muri abo batware agenda avuga icye. Umwami yumvise hari abatware bifuriza rubanda ibihano birimo ubugome, maze asanze bikabije buri wese amuhanisha icyo yagiye avuga.<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Umutware witwaga Kamegeri, we yari yavuze ko igihano cyiza ari ugusambura inzu ziri hafi aho, bagacaniriza urutare iyo sakamburiro kugeza aho urutare rutukura, noneho umuntu w\\u2019umugome bakarumushyiraho agashirira. Umwami nyuma yo gutekereza kuri icyo gihano, yasanze nta muntu mubi (w\\u2019umugome) kurusha Kamegeri. Nuko aca iteka ko uwo Kamegeri bamuhanisha icyo gihano kibi yahimbiye abandi, noneho baramuboha bamujugunya ari muzima ku rutare bacaniriye rwatukuye nk\\u2019uko yabyifurizaga abandi.<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Burya koko ngo umwami ntiyica, hica abamuhuza na rubanda kandi nabo ari rubanda! Mu buzima busanzwe, hari ubwo abantu usanga bifuriza abandi ibibi nk\\u2019uko Kamegeri yabikoze, ibyo bikaba byabatera kugambanira abandi, kubateranya ku bayobozi cyangwa abandi babakuriye, bakifuza ko ikibi cyaba ku bandi. Ibi ariko abateye batyo bakwiye kubyitondera, bakamenya ko hari ubwo ikibi wifuriza abandi nawe gishobora kukugeraho.<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Ku bemera Imana, kwifuriza abandi ibibi bikuzanira umuvumo ariko kwifuza ko na mugenzi wawe yagira umugisha akagira amahoro n\\u2019iterambere, ibyo ubwabyo ni byiza kuri wowe kuko bikuzanira imigisha. Ntabwo kugirira ishyari umuntu ku bw\\u2019umugisha afite bizatuma umugisha we uba uwawe, ahubwo bishobora kuzakwambura n\\u2019umugisha wowe wari wisanganiwe.<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Umunsi umwe, Gisanura yabajije abatware be igihano gisumba ibindi, buri wese agenda avuga icye. Umwami asanze bikabije, buri wese amuhanisha icyo yagiye avuga. Nguko uko umwe wari watahuye ko igihano cyiza ari ugusambura inzu ziri hafi, bagacaniriza urutare iyo sakamburiro kugeza aho urutare rutukura, noneho umugome bakarumushyiraho agashirira. Ibyo byahimbwe n\\u2019umutware witwaga Kamegeri. Umwami yasanze nta muntu mubi (w\\u2019umugome) kurusha Kamegeri.<\\/p><div class=\\\"thumb tright\\\" align=\\\"left\\\"><div class=\\\"thumbinner\\\"><div class=\\\"thumbcaption\\\">Urutare rwa Kamegeri bamaze kurucanira<\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><div align=\\\"left\\\"><p>Nuko aca iteka ko uwo Kamegeri bamuhanisha icyo gihano kibi yahimbiye abandi. Noneho baramuboha bamujugunya ari muzima ku rutare bacaniriye rwatukuye.<\\/p><div>\\u00a0<\\/div><div><img class=\\\"artimgv5 img-responsive\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L860xH286\\/urutare-rwa-kamegeri-b0eff.gif?1493381638\\\" width=\\\"860\\\" height=\\\"286\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" \\/><\\/div><div><p><img class=\\\"artimgv5 img-responsive\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L719xH285\\/sdfsd-d6a61.jpg?1493381638\\\" width=\\\"719\\\" height=\\\"285\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" \\/><\\/p><div class=\\\"gh_articlep_dphotos\\\" align=\\\"center\\\">Bivugwa ko uru rutare kera rwatukuraga nyuma y\'aho rutwikiweho umutware Kamegeri<\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><p align=\\\"left\\\">Uru rutare ruri mu Karere ka Ruhango rufite amateka menshi; aha niho umutware Kamegeri yatwikiwe ku ngoma y\\u2019umwami Mibambwe Sekarongoro Mutabazi nyuma y\\u2019aho asabiye iki gihano abanyabyaha.<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Uru rutare kuva icyo gihe rwahise rumwitirirwa, kandi bivugwa ko kuva icyo gihe rwakomeje gutukura.<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Binavugwa kandi ko uru rutare rwabagaho nta zina rugira ariko kuva aho rutwikiweho Kamegeri rwakomeje kujya rumwitirirwa mu kwibuka uko yari umutware w\\u2019umugome cyane wafataga ibyemezo bikarishye kugeza ubwo urwo yaciriye uwari wagomeye umwami ari we ruhitanye atwikirwa ku rutare.<\\/p><p align=\\\"left\\\">Ese ni gute utasura aha hantu, ngo wiyumvire ubuhamya bw\\u2019abahatuye?<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
