(1295, 554, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"tmdlqlr\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ggczdpb\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ndfjmxo\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Mu rwego rwo kwimakaza umuco wo gutarama no guhiga nk\\u2019imwe mu nzira zo kugaruka ku isoko y\\u2019umurage w\\u2019u Rwanda no kuwuhesha agaciro\\u00a0, Itorero Indahigwa za IPRC gihugu ryateguye igitaramo cyiswe \\u201cIndahigwa Twataramye\\u201d.<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-547\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/GRN9165-300x200.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"200\\\" \\/><\\/p><p>Abagize Indahigwa bateguye igitaramo cy\\u2019inkera\\u00a0 kizabera kuri IPRS ya Kigali -Kicukiro\\u00a0 ku itariki ya 15 Ukuboza 2017\\u00a0 guhera saa kumi nebyri nigice z\\u2019umugoroba.<\\/p>[caption id=\\\"attachment_548\\\" align=\\\"alignnone\\\" width=\\\"300\\\"]<img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-548\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/GRN9192-300x167.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"167\\\" \\/> Indahigwa[\\/caption]<p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p>Indahigwa\\u00a0 ni itorero ndangamuco rya IPRS ryashinzwe mu mwaka wa 2015<\\/p><p>NDAHIRIWE Emmy umuyobozi wa Indahigwa\\u00a0, yabwiye umucowacu.com ,\\u201cIki gitaramo cy\\u2019Inkera y\\u2019Abahizi gihishiye abazacyitabira kubasubiza ku muzi w\\u2019umuco wo gutarama no guhiga mu Rwanda. Imbyino, Imihamirizo, umurishyo w\\u2019ingoma, n\\u2019indirimbo byose biherekejwe n\\u2019ibicurangisho gakondo bizumvinkanisha urwunge rw\\u2019amajwi y\\u2019indashyikirwa,\\u201d.<\\/p>[caption id=\\\"attachment_549\\\" align=\\\"alignnone\\\" width=\\\"300\\\"]<img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-549\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/IMG-20171212-WA0012-300x300.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"300\\\" \\/> Umuyozi w\'Indahigwa[\\/caption]<p>akomeza atubwira ko Intego yigitaramo ari \\\"<strong>Uruhare rw\'urubyiruko mugusigasira umuco nyarwanda\\\"<\\/strong><\\/p><p><img class=\\\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-553\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/GRN9177-300x200.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"200\\\" \\/><\\/p><p>Indahigwa\\u00a0 ni abasore n\'inkumi 45 biyemeje kwimakaza umuco<\\/p><p>Igitaramo kizabera kuri IPRS kwinjira\\u00a0 ku itariki ya 15 Ukuboza 2017\\u00a0 guhera saa kumi nebyri nigice z\\u2019umugoroba,ni ubuntu<\\/p><p>Indahigwa za IPRS niryo torero ryahize andi yaza kaminuza\\u00a0 riza kumwanya\\u00a0 wa mbere muri uyu mwaka .<\\/p><p>Uwasha Indahigwa yazisanga kuri IPRS Kigali aho zitaramira buri wese ndetse nuwabashaka ngo basurutse ibirori niho yabasanga<\\/p><p>Abandi bazaba muri ikigitaramo harimo\\u00a0Umusore w\'umunyarwanda\\u00a0<em>Deo Munyakazi<\\/em>, uzobereye mu gucuranga inanga nyarwanda,ukunzwe cyane nabatari bakeya\\u00a0<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-550\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/Copy-of-DSC_7282-300x199.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"199\\\" \\/>Munyakazi Deo azaba akirigita inanga<\\/p><p>UMVA HANO:<\\/p><h1 class=\\\"title style-scope ytd-video-primary-info-renderer\\\">Isoko Dusangiye ya Deo Munyakazi<\\/h1><p><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=m1SwVtruaz8\\\">https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=m1SwVtruaz8<\\/a><\\/p><p>Muri ikigitaramo kandi hazaba harimo Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier nawe ukunzwe cyane nabenshi.\\u00a0<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-551\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/IMG-20170708-WA0007-200x300.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"200\\\" height=\\\"300\\\" \\/><\\/p><h1 class=\\\"title style-scope ytd-video-primary-info-renderer\\\">Niba ari Ibyo nta Rwanda ya\\u00a0 Tuyisenge Olivier<\\/h1><p><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=uaMkjwV8Ayo\\\">https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=uaMkjwV8Ayo<\\/a><\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p>Itorero Indahigwa\\u00a0 ryashinzwe mu mwaka wa 2015, rifite inshingano yo guteza imbere umurage gakondo w\\u2019u Rwanda mu mbyino n\\u2019indirimbo gakondo.<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-552\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/Indahigwa-Twataramye1-300x300.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"300\\\" \\/><\\/p><div class=\\\"mceTemp\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
