\\"300\\\" \\/> Umuyozi w\'Indahigwa[\\/caption]<p>akomeza atubwira ko Intego yigitaramo ari \\\"<strong>Uruhare rw\'urubyiruko mugusigasira umuco nyarwanda\\\"<\\/strong><\\/p><p><img class=\\\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-553\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/GRN9177-300x200.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"200\\\" \\/><\\/p><p>Indahigwa\\u00a0 ni abasore n\'inkumi 45 biyemeje kwimakaza umuco<\\/p><p>Igitaramo kizabera kuri IPRS ku itariki ya 15 Ukuboza 2017\\u00a0 guhera saa kumi nebyri nigice z\\u2019umugoroba, kwinjira\\u00a0 ni ubuntu<\\/p><p>Indahigwa za IPRS niryo torero ryahize andi yaza kaminuza\\u00a0 riza kumwanya\\u00a0 wa mbere muri uyu mwaka .<\\/p><p>Uwashaka\\u00a0 Indahigwa yazisanga kuri IPRS Kigali aho zitaramira buri wese ndetse nushaka ko ibirori bye bisusuruka\\u00a0 niho yabasanga<\\/p>[caption id=\\\"attachment_552\\\" align=\\\"alignnone\\\" width=\\\"300\\\"]<img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-552\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/Indahigwa-Twataramye1-300x300.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"300\\\" \\/> Urupapuro rwamamaza igitaramo[\\/caption]<p>Abandi bazaba muri ikigitaramo harimo\\u00a0Umusore w\'umunyarwanda\\u00a0<em>Deo Munyakazi<\\/em>, uzobereye mu gucuranga inanga nyarwanda,ukunzwe cyane nabatari bakeya\\u00a0<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-550\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/Copy-of-DSC_7282-300x199.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"199\\\" \\/><\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p>Munyakazi Deo azaba akirigita inanga<\\/p><p>UMVA HANO:<\\/p><h1 class=\\\"title style-scope ytd-video-primary-info-renderer\\\">Isoko Dusangiye ya Deo Munyakazi<\\/h1><p><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=m1SwVtruaz8\\\">https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=m1SwVtruaz8<\\/a><\\/p><p>Muri ikigitaramo kandi hazaba harimo Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier nawe ukunzwe cyane nabenshi.\\u00a0<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-551\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/IMG-20170708-WA0007-200x300.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"200\\\" height=\\\"300\\\" \\/><\\/p><h1 class=\\\"title style-scope ytd-video-primary-info-renderer\\\">Umva HAno:Niba ari Ibyo nta Rwanda ya\\u00a0 Tuyisenge Olivier<\\/h1><p><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=uaMkjwV8Ayo\\\">https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=uaMkjwV8Ayo<\\/a><\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p>Itorero Indahigwa\\u00a0 ryashinzwe mu mwaka wa 2015, rifite inshingano yo guteza imbere umurage gakondo w\\u2019u Rwanda mu mbyino n\\u2019indirimbo gakondo.<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-552\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/umucowacu.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/Indahigwa-Twataramye1-300x300.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"300\\\" \\/><\\/p><div class=\\\"mceTemp\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div><p>Igitaramo kizabera kuri IPRS ku itariki ya 15 Ukuboza 2017\\u00a0 guhera saa kumi nebyri nigice z\\u2019umugoroba, kwinjira\\u00a0 ni ubuntu<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
