(1371, 565, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"frgtsjg\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"fvvtblo\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"jnpcnet\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<div class=\\\"col col-lg-7 col-md-7 col-sm-7 col-xs-7\\\"><p>Abakobwa bifuza guhatanira ikamba rya Nyampinga w\\u2019u Rwanda 2018 baratangira kwiyandikisha mu ijoro ryo kuri uyu wa Gatatu, rikaba ari irushanwa ririmo impinduka mu mitegurire, abazaryitabira n\\u2019aho rizabera.<\\/p><\\/div><div class=\\\"col col-lg-12\\\"><div class=\\\"fulltext margintop10\\\"><p>Itorwa rya Miss Rwanda ryateguwe na Mashirika muri 2012, na ho kuva mu mwaka wa 2014 isoko ryatsindiwe na Rwanda Inspiration Backup ku bufatanye n\\u2019abaterankunga baryo ku isonga hari Cogebanque, ari na bo batangiye igikorwa cyo gushaka Nyampinga 2018 uzasimbura Iradukunda Elsa.<\\/p><p>Nk\\u2019uko Ishimwe uyobora Rwanda Inspiration Backup yabitangaje mu kiganiro n\\u2019itangazamakuru cyabaye kuri uyu wa Gatatu tariki 13 Ukuboza 2017, kuva saa sita z\\u2019ijoro, abakobwa bifuza guhatanira ikamba rya Nyampinga w\\u2019u Rwanda, baratangira kwiyandikisha banyuze ku rubuga rwa \\u2018Miss Rwanda\\u2019.<\\/p><p>Ibikorwa by\\u2019ijonjora bizatangira tariki 13 Mutarama 2018 mu Karere ka Musanze, tariki 14 Mutarama 2018 bikomereze mu Karere ka Rubavu, ku ya 20 Mutarama 2018 ni mu Karere ka Huye, tariki 21 Mutarama 2018 bikomereze mu Karere ka Kayonza bikazasorezwa mu Mujyi wa Kigali tariki 27 Mutarama 2018.<\\/p><p>Ishimwe yatangaje ko uyu mwaka Miss Rwanda izagaragaramo impinduka zitandukanye zirimo ko mu majonjora hazatoranywa abakobwa 30 aho kuba 25 nk\\u2019uko byari bisanzwe nyuma hakazakorwa irindi jonjora rizasigazamo abakobwa 20. Aba nibo bazerekeza mu mwiherero aho kuba 15 bari basanzwe bajyamo.<\\/p><p>Yagize ati \\u201cIzi ni impinduka zigamije kudufasha kubona Miss Rwanda iva ku rwego rumwe ikajya ku rundi. No mu mwiherero hazakorwa bya bikorwa basanzwe bakora birimo kwiga umuco, kumenya igihugu cyabo ariko noneho hazajya hakorwa n\\u2019ikizamini mbere y\\u2019uko umuntu agera ku munsi wa nyuma w\\u2019irushanwa.\\u201d<\\/p><p>Yakomeje agira ati \\u201cNi ikizamini cyanditse aho umuntu azabazwa ibibazo bisanzwe hakanababo ikiganiro [interview] aho buri mukobwa azajya abazwa n\\u2019akanama nkemurampaka ku buryo yifuza ko umushinga we wafasha Abanyarwanda. Hazabaho gutora kuri sms ndetse harebwe n\\u2019imyitwarire y\\u2019umukobwa, uko abana n\\u2019abandi, umuco n\\u2019indangagaciro.\\u201d<\\/p><p>Izindi mpinduka ziri mu irushanwa rya 2018 ni uko umubare w\\u2019ibisonga bya Nyampinga wavuye kuri bine hakazatoranywa bibiri gusa.<\\/p><p>Ishimwe yavuze ko bitewe n\\u2019uko buri mukobwa yasaga n\\u2019ukora umushinga we ku giti cye, noneho bazatoranya imishinga itatu bakayikorera hamwe bikaba ari yo mpamvu umubare w\\u2019ibisonga wagabanutse.<\\/p><p><strong><em><img class=\\\" b-loaded\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/inyarwanda.com\\/img\\/201712\\/attachments\\/1513169455__dsc0710.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Miss Rwanda 2018\\\" \\/>\\u00a0<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p><p>Ibirori byo gutora Miss Rwanda byakuwe mu ihema rya Camp Kigali kuri iyi nshuro bikazabera muri Kigali Convention Center ndetse n\\u2019amasaha bimara akaba yaragabanyijwe, atazongera kurenga abiri n\\u2019igice.<\\/p><p><strong>Ibisabwa kugira ngo umukobwa yiyandikishirize guhatanira ikamba rya Miss Rwanda 2018:<\\/strong><\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba ari Umunyarwandakazi<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba afite hagati y\\u2019imyaka 18-24<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba yararangije amashuri yisumbuye<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba avuga neza Ikinyarwanda n\\u2019urundi rurimi, hagati y\\u2019Icyongereza, Igifaransa n\\u2019Igiswahili<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba afite indeshyo ya sentimetero 170 kuzamura<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba apima ibiro hagati ya 45-70<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba atari yabyara<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba yiteguye kumara nibura umwaka atuye mu Rwanda, igihe yatsinze<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba atiteguye gukora ubukwe mu gihe cy\\u2019umwaka yambaye ikamba<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba yiteguye guhagararira u Rwanda mu gihe bikenewe<\\/p><\\/div><p>Mu bihembo Nyampinga azahabwa harimo imodoka nshya ya Suzuki n\\u2019umushahara w\\u2019ibihumbi 800 by\\u2019amafaranga y\\u2019u Rwanda bizatangwa na Cogebanque, amatike y\\u2019indege azatangwa na RwandAir, kumwishyurira salon akoreshamo imisatsi umwaka, kumwambika igihe cyose agiye mu marushanwa, kumwishyurira internet y\\u2019umwaka n\\u2019ibindi.<\\/p><p><img class=\\\" b-loaded\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/inyarwanda.com\\/img\\/201712\\/attachments\\/1513169454__dsc0696.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Miss Rwanda 2018\\\" width=\\\"810\\\" height=\\\"542\\\" \\/><\\/p><\\/div><div class=\\\"col col-lg-12\\\"><p><strong><em><img class=\\\" b-loaded\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/inyarwanda.com\\/img\\/201712\\/attachments\\/1513169455__dsc0710.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Miss Rwanda 2018\\\" \\/><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p><p><strong><em>Miss Iradukunda n\'abategura Miss Rwanda ubwo bari imbere y\'abanyamakuru<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p><p><img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-25660 td-animation-stack-type0-1\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; width: 640px; display: block; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\\" title=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/i0.wp.com\\/www.touchrwanda.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/IMG_1131.jpg?resize=640%2C427\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\\\" srcset=\\\"https:\\/\\/i0.wp.com\\/www.touchrwanda.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/IMG_1131.jpg?w=640 640w, https:\\/\\/i0.wp.com\\/www.touchrwanda.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/IMG_1131.jpg?resize=300%2C200 300w, https:\\/\\/i0.wp.com\\/www.touchrwanda.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/IMG_1131.jpg?resize=630%2C420 630w\\\" alt=\\\"Itangazamakuru ryari ryiganje muri iki kiganiro\\\" width=\\\"640\\\" height=\\\"427\\\" data-attachment-id=\\\"25660\\\" data-permalink=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.touchrwanda.com\\/2017\\/12\\/miss-rwanda-2018-yiganjemo-impinduka-zidasanzwe\\/img_1131\\/\\\" data-orig-file=\\\"https:\\/\\/i0.wp.com\\/www.touchrwanda.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/IMG_1131.jpg?fit=640%2C427\\\" data-orig-size=\\\"640,427\\\" data-comments-opened=\\\"1\\\" data-image-meta=\\\"{\\\" data-image-title=\\\"IMG_1131\\\" data-image-description=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/p><p>Itangazamakuru ryari ryiganje muri iki kiganiro<\\/p><\\/div>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
