\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba yararangije amashuri yisumbuye<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba avuga neza Ikinyarwanda n\\u2019urundi rurimi, hagati y\\u2019Icyongereza, Igifaransa n\\u2019Igiswahili<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba afite indeshyo ya sentimetero 170 kuzamura<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba apima ibiro hagati ya 45-70<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba atari yabyara<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba yiteguye kumara nibura umwaka atuye mu Rwanda, igihe yatsinze<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba atiteguye gukora ubukwe mu gihe cy\\u2019umwaka yambaye ikamba<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"puce\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/igihe.com\\/local\\/cache-vignettes\\/L8xH11\\/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\\\" alt=\\\"-\\\" width=\\\"8\\\" height=\\\"11\\\" \\/>\\u00a0Kuba yiteguye guhagararira u Rwanda mu gihe bikenewe<\\/p><\\/div><p>Mu bihembo Nyampinga azahabwa harimo imodoka nshya ya Suzuki n\\u2019umushahara w\\u2019ibihumbi 800 by\\u2019amafaranga y\\u2019u Rwanda biz