(40, 1, '2015-03-20 06:41:07', '2015-03-20 06:41:07', '<b>Umuhanzi Kaneza Sheja wamaze gushyira ahagaragara indirimbo “Kagame Karambe” ivuga ibigwi by’umukuru w’igihugu Perezida Paul Kagame.</b>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\"><b>Umuhanzi Kaneza Sheja</b> uri mu cyiciro cyanyuma umwaka wa gatanu mu ishuri ry’umuziki ku Nyundo ndetse wamaze gushyira ahagaragara indirimbo “<b>Kagame Karambe”</b> ivuga ibigwi by’umukuru w’igihugu <b>Perezida Paul Kagame</b>, yemeza  byakabaye ngombwa abahanzi bose bagaca mu ishuri ry’umuziki kuko bibafasha kuyobora neza impano bafite no guhanga ibyubaka igihugu bifite umumaro.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><b>Kaneza  Sheja</b> witegura guhabwa impamyabumenyi muri muzika,yemeza ko yagiye kwiga muzika nyuma yo kubwirwa na benshi ndetse akabona ko afite impano y’ubuhanzi yabonye adashobora kuyiyobora neza atanyuze mu ishuri ngo amenye indagagaciro na kirazira zizamuyobora. Nyuma yo kwiga muri iri shuri  ryo ku Nyundo ,Kaneza yemeza ko yasobanukiwe ibyo akora ndetse amenya kubitandukanya n’ibyo yarazi  no guha abanyarwanda ibintu bisobanutse kandi bishyitse.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://kigalihit.rw/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/13315394_634245976727445_7265419093409892166_n.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-30733\" src=\"http://kigalihit.rw/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/13315394_634245976727445_7265419093409892166_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"619\" height=\"412\" /></a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">Kuri ubu uyu muhanzi Kaneza isheja yemeza ko nyuma yaho ahimbiye iyi ndirimbo byatumye akabya inzozi dore ko yemeza ko, yabonye iterambere ryihuse kandi rifatika ry\'uburyo bwose haba mukubona abakunzi benshi ndetse n\'iterambere  ry\'ibifatika.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">Kaneza numwe mu bahanzi bakomeye baririmba indirimbo zibanda ku muco,kandi akagira umwihariko ndetse  ibihangano bye abihanga\r\nagendeye ku ndangagaciro na kirazira ari nayo mpamvu  yemeza ko ibyo\r\naririmba bigomba kugira ireme haba mu\r\nmiririmbire,imyandikire,<wbr />imicurangire n’ijwi.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">Ikindi twavuga kuri uyu muhanzi intore idasobanya Kaneza ubu yabaye uwa mbere mu Turere dutanfukanye aho agomba kwamamariza Umu candidat wa <b>RPF</b> mu turere dukurikira:\r\nRusizi\r\nKarongi\r\nRubavu\r\nKayonza.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://kigalihit.rw/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Captureaaa.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-30735\" src=\"http://kigalihit.rw/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Captureaaa.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"541\" height=\"555\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<div align=\"left\">Mukiganiro Kaneza yagiranye na <a href=\"http://umucowacu.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://umucowacu.com&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1500017902875000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFqC1sE41WINQZDdt_tg3Umx8TxBQ\">umucowacu.com</a>akomeza yibutsa abafana be ndetse n\'abandi bose gukomeza kumushyigikira ndetse no gukomeza gutunga indirimbo ye <b>\'\' KAGAME KARAMBE\'</b>\'  asoza abwira abakunzi be ko kubaka u Rwanda ari inshingano ya buri wese ati kandi guhitamo neza niyo nkingi yabyose. Kaneza asoza asezeranya abakunzi be ko indirimbo zirimo ubutumwa bwo kwiyubakira igihugu zizaba zigeze hanze vuba aha ziherekejwe na amashusho ya \"KAGAME KARAMBE\".</div>', 'Kaneza Sheja ati:“Kagame Karambe”  Yumve HANO', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'kayaking-adventurous-sport', '', '', '2017-12-04 08:30:06', '2017-12-04 08:30:06', '', 0, 'http://demo.themegrill.com/colormag/?p=40', 0, 'post', '', 0),
