(111, 1, '2015-03-24 07:44:03', '2015-03-24 07:44:03', '<b>Amateka n’umuco ni bimwe mu bintu biha umwimerere igihugu, umuryango cyangwa igice cy’abaturage runaka. Hari uburyo bwinshi amateka agenda ahererekanwamo, ntazimangatane yewe n’ubwo haba hashize imyaka myinshi.</b>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>Nyagakecuru  wari utuye mu bisi bya Huye ubu biri mu karere ka Huye. Nyagakecuru uyu  ubusanzwe izina rye ryari Benginzage akaba yari umugore w’umugabo witwa Samukende.</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Amateka akunda kumuvuga nk’umugore wari ukomeye  kandi uzwi cyane kuruta umugabo we Samukende. Samukende amateka ntagaragaza ibigwi bye yewe ntanagaragaza niba yarabaye umwami  w’iyo mpugu yariku mukika w’umusozi wa Huye kumanuka ugana Nyakibanda y’abaseminali kugeza ku Burundi.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>Ingoma y’Ubungwe (Abenengwe)</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Iki gihugu cyari gikikijwe  mu majyepfo n’uruzi rw’Akanyaru  intara ya Ngozi na Kayanza, mu Rwanda cyri gikikijwe  na Buganza y’epfo, Bashumba na Nyakare.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Gusa Nyagakecuru uvugwa mu ngoma y’abenengwe  yari umwamikazi (umugore w’umwami) w’igihugu cyitwaga Bungwe. Ingoma ngabe yabo yitwaga  Nyamibande. Ubwoko bwabo bwari abenengwe ikirangabwoko cyabo ari ingwe.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Cyari igihugu gikomeye ku buryo ku ngoma y’abanyiginya mu rwanda byari byarananiranye kwigarurira u Bungwe.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>Iyo hataba amayeri yo gutanga igitambo  igihugu cya Nyagakecuru nticyari kwigarurirwa</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Urugamba rwo kwigarurira u Bungwe rwatangiye ahagana ku ngoma ya Ruganzu. Bimwe  mu bitekerezo byo kwagura ingoma nyiginya bigaragaza ko u Bungwe (igihugu cya Nyagakecuru ) cyaba cyarigaruriwe na Ruganzu Ndoli.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Ikirari cyo kwigarurira  iyo ngoma kivugwa ku ngoma ya Yuhi II Gahima. Yuhi II gahima yari  umuhungu wa Mibambwe I Sekarongoro I Mutabazi. Uyu ni we watangiye uburyo bwo gushaka  uko yazigarurira igihugu cy’u Bungwe.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong> Uko byagenze</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Mu gushaka uko igihugu cy’Abenengwe cyatsindwa n’ u Rwanda yashatse gukoresha inzira y’ubucengeri(ubutabazi). Abapfumu bagaragaje ko kugirango u Bungwe butsindwe murumuna wa Nyagakecuru witwaga Nyankaka agomba kujya kwa  Samukende akaba mukeba wa mukuruwe hanyuma umwana wa mbere akazamubyarira mu rwanda ku buryo ari we uzatsinda u Bungwe.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Mu kugenza gutyo  hateganywaga ko nibura umwuzukuru wa Gahima ari we wagombaga kugira uruhare mu kwigarurira u Bungwe.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Nyankaka yagiye kwa Samukende aramurongora ariko atazi icyari kigambiriwe. Amaze gutwara inda yagarutse i Rwanda  ahabyaririra umuhungu wiswe Binama.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Uyu Binama aho amariye gukurira ni we wagiye gutabarira u rwanda Bucengeri. Nyuma  ni ho u Bungwe bwafashwe ndetse buratsindwa. Ingoma ngabe Nyamibande ifatwa ubwo.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Amateka y’ imitsindirwe  ya Bungwe ihurizwa ku bami babiri aribo Ruganzu wa II Ndoli n’umuhungu we Mutara I Semugeshi bitaga Muyenzi.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><em>Twibukiranye amateka y\'ibi bisi bya Huye</em></strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Ibisi ubundi mu Kinyarwanda bisobanura uruhererekane rw’imisozi. Ibisi bya Huye, kuri ubu biherereye mu karere ka Huye mu ntara y’Amajyepfo, ni umusozi muremure ufite ubutumburuke bugera kuri metero 2400. Ni ahantu hateye amabengeza dore ko ugeze mu bushorishori bw’uyu musozi asanganirwa n’akayaga gahuhera ndetse n’isura nziza y’indi misozi migufi kuri uyu. Kuwuzamuka bisaba iminota iri hagati ya 50 na 60 n’amaguru. Uyu musozi wambaye ishyamba ririmo ibiti bitandukanye ibyinshi bya kimeza, ibiti byambika uyu musozi ubwiza ndetse n’amahumbezi  adasanzwe.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><em>Uwo Nyagakecuru wahatuye we ni muntu ki?</em></strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Uyu Nyagakecuru yamenyekanye cyane ku ngoma y’umwami Ruganzu wa II Ndoli. Yari umugore ubundi witwaga Beginzage afite umugabo witwaga Samukende. Amateka ntagaruka cyane kuri uyu mugabo wa Beginzage, nyamara ahubwo agaruka kuri Beginzage wari warahimbwe Nyagakecuru nyine, nyuma yo kwigomeka ndetse no kuzengereza uyu mwami Ruganzu.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Uku kwigomeka kwatangiye ubwo umwami Ruganzu yashakaga kwigarurira igihugu cy’Ubungwe, ari na cyo Nyagakecuru uwo yari abereye umwamikazi, ubwoko bw’abo mu bungwe bwari Abenengwe. Bungwe.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Uyu Nyagakecuru rero ngo yari yaranze gutanga amaturo ajya i bwami nk’uko abandi baturage babigenzaga, nuko birakaza umwami, dore ko n’ubwo umwami yajyaga yohereza ingabo gutera uyu mugore, zose zatsindwaga.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Itongo ry’uyu Nyagakecuru riri mu bushorishori bw’uyu musozi.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><em>Reka dutemberane ibisi bya Huye mu mafoto noneho:</em></strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">     <em>Amafu atangwa n’ibiti biri kuri uyu musozi bituma uwuzamuka atumva umunaniro cyane</em></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335569_b30a9159_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img title=\"undefined\" src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335569_b30a9159_copy.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><em>Uyu musozi wambaye ishyamba ry’ibiti bitandukanye</em></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>Reka twihute tugere ku bushorishori, kuko ibanga ry’aha ni ho rizingiye...</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Twegere hirya gato dusure itongo rya Nyagakecuru wavuzwe haruguru. Birumvikana ko tutari buhasange inzu ye cyangwa se ibindi bimenyetso binini byerekana ko hari hatuwe, nyamara haragaragara.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335570_b30a9185_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img title=\"undefined\" src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335570_b30a9185_copy.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><em>Ng\'ibi ibiti byo mu bwoko bw’ibitovu byaba mu marembo y’urugo rwe, bivugwa ko byari birebire</em></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Nyagakecuru, uvugwaho kuba yari afite izindi mbaraga zidasanzwe (ibirozi), ngo yaba yari afite inzoka nini zamurindaga zari zituriye mu rugo iwe. Ntagoo turi bubashe kuzibona, ariko imyobo yazo yo turayibona.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335828_b30a9192_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img title=\"undefined\" src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335828_b30a9192_copy.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335828_b30a9193_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img title=\"undefined\" src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335828_b30a9193_copy.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"> <em>Ng\'iyi imyobo izo nzoka za Nyagakecuru zari zituyemo ubwo yari ariho</em></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Nyagakecuru kandi yari afite aho yajyaga kwisukurira, aho yajyanaga n’abaja be nuko akajya kwiyuhagira. Twigiye hirya gato, turahasanga iryo riba.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335828_b30a9199_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img title=\"undefined\" src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335828_b30a9199_copy.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><em>Iriba Nyagakecuru yajyaga kwiyuhagiriraho n’ubu riracyahari mu ishusho y’ikizenga cy’amazi.</em></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><em> </em>Nyuma yo gusobanukirwa n’amateka ya Nyagakecuru, reka noneho dutembere ubushorishori bw’uyu musozi.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335829_b30a9216_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img title=\"undefined\" src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335829_b30a9216_copy.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335982_b30a9302_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img title=\"undefined\" src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335982_b30a9302_copy.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><em>Mu bushorishori wakirwa n’utwatsi duherereye turushaho kongera ubwiza bw’aha hantu</em></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335829_b30a9218_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img title=\"undefined\" src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335829_b30a9218_copy.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><em>Hakurya ibiti byiza biteye amabengeza biterausuye hano hantu gusubiranayo akanyamuneza</em></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335981_b30a9224_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img title=\"undefined\" src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335981_b30a9224_copy.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><em>Hakurya, indi misozi yongera isura nziza y’aha hantu</em></p>', 'Amateka ya Nyagakecuru wo mu bisi bya Huye', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'amateka-ya-nyagakecuru-wo-mu-bisi-bya-huye', '', '', '2017-12-04 10:19:31', '2017-12-04 10:19:31', '', 0, 'http://demo.themegrill.com/colormag/?p=111', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(114, 1, '2015-03-24 07:47:05', '2015-03-24 07:47:05', '<b>Poetic fever ni igitaramo cy\'ubusizi cyabaye ku mugoroba wo kuri uyu gatandatu tariki ya 16 Nzeri i Kigali muri Blue Note.</b>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Transpoesis yari isanzwe imenyerewe mu gutegura amarushanwa nayo y\'ubusizi yiswe Kigali Vibrates with Poetry amarushanwa ngaruka gihembwe. Kuri ubu Transpoesis igiye kujya ifatanya ibyo bikorwa\r\nbyombi ari amarushanwa ndetse ni iki gitaramo poetic fever kizajya kiba ngarukakwezi nkuko twabitangarijwe na Dr Andrea Grieder umuyobozi wa Transpoesis.</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZYIKTEY.jpg\" width=\"515\" /></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Poetic Fever ni igitaramo cyatangiye ahagana ku i saa mbili z\'umugoroba mu mujyi wa Kigali rwagati mu Kabari kitwa Blue Note,maze ku ikubitiro Kivumbi cyangwa Lion King abimburira abandi basizi\r\nbinyura imbaga mu gisigo cye kiri mu rurimi rw\'icyongereza yise\" King meet</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">  king\",igitaramo cyaje gukomeza maze abasizi bagiye batandukanye barimo Bahati Innocent, Ella Bikwemu,Delice Mukazi,Carine Maniraguha,Andrea Grieder,Amina Umuhoza, Esther Uwibambe basusurutsa abitabiriye poetic fever karahava.\r\nNyuma y\' igitaramo ikinyamakuru umuco wacu cyaganiriye numwe mu basizi\r\nbitabiriye iki gitaramo ari we Kivumbi(Lion King) atangaza uko\r\nyiyumva. Yatangiye agira ati&lt;&lt; Ku nshuro ya mbere nishimiye ubwitabire bw\'abantu muri iki gitaramo ikindi ndashimira cyane Dr Andrea Grieder\r\nkubw\'uru rubuga yashyiriyeho abasizi Imana imuhe umugisha,ndagira ngo kandi mbwire abakunda ubusizi ko bashonje bahishiwe kuko ibikorwa byo ni byinshi&gt;&gt;.</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ATqqPOp.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4aDDypI.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Dr Andrea Grieder</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/f9GaDCQ.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Iki gitaramo kikaba cyari gifite umwihariko wuko buri musizi wese\r\nyacurangirwaga ibisigo bye abifashijwemo na Band yitwa Kinga Blues\r\nihagarariwe n\'umunyamuziki ukomoka mu gihugu cy\'Uburundi Arnauld\r\nNganji.</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><b> REBA AMAFOTO</b>:</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Kw5hC8s.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MHXZpwE.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/91gjU4z.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zlbFPXo.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9zWMpSn.jpg\" width=\"424\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VPLujVX.jpg\" width=\"499\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SFalW9I.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6SD3pUa.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q1jwn1d.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0OxzOdA.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eZgM219.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/P96IGZu.jpg\" width=\"395\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cUvJKxZ.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OlawOhC.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/77LsBYj.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yVRf0GB.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">ntagihindutse igitaramo \"<b>Poetic Fever</b>\" kizongera kuba ku\r\nwa 14 Ukwakira uyu mwaka nubundi muri Blue Note.</div>', 'Transpoesis yamaze gukora ikindi gitaramo cy\'ubusizi yise \'\'Poetic Fever\'\'.AMAFOTO', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'invention-of-advance-technology', '', '', '2017-12-09 12:27:22', '2017-12-09 12:27:22', '', 0, 'http://demo.themegrill.com/colormag/?p=114', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(117, 1, '2015-03-24 07:52:02', '2015-03-24 07:52:02', '<p><b>Abagize itsinda ComponentsRw rigizwe n\' umuvangavangamiziki(Dj) Karengera Kirenga Eric Soul, umukirigitananga Munyakazi Deo, abaraperi babiri aribo Mazimpaka Prime na Angel Mutoni, guhera kuri uyu wa 22 Nzeri 2017 barabarizwa mu murwa mukuru w\'igihugu cy\'Ubugande Kampala aho bitabiriye iserukiramuco ryitwa Bayimba Festival.</b></p>itsinda  ComponentsRw bahagurutse i Kigali mu gitondo cyo<br /> kuri uyu wa Gatanu berekeza mu gihugu cya Uganda ahagiye kubera iri<br /> serukiramuco rya Bayimba Festival rigiye kuba ku ncuro ya cumi, rikaba<br /> ryitabiriwe n\'abahanzi baturutse mu bihugu bitandukanye ku isi. Iri<br /> tsinda rihagarariye u Rwanda biteganyijwe ko riri bususurutse<br /> abitabiriye iri serukiramuco uyu munsi tariki ya 23/ Nzeri 2017 guhera<br /> i saa tatu z\'ijoro ku isaha yo mu bugande n\'ukuvuga saa mbili z\'ijoro<br /> ku isaha yo mu Rwanda.<p>Aba bahanzi baratangaza ko nyuma yo kugera Uganda amahoro bameze neza<br /> ko biteguye kuza gutarama bagacyura inganji nkuko Munyakazi Deo umwe<br /> mu bahanzi bagize itsinda ComponentsRw yabitangarije ikinyamakuru<br /> umucowacu.com Yatangiye agira ati \"Mukuri turiteguye cyane,twagerageje<br /> gukora imyitozo ihagije pee!! Ndagira ngo niba hari abanyarwanda bari<br /> inaha bakunda umuziki w\'umwimerere bazi kuza badushyigikire twe nka<br /> ComponentsRw duhagaze bwuma\".</p> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iynUhcb.jpg\" width=\"388\" height=\"388\" /><p>                              MUNYAKAZI DEO</p> <p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lg6gvIB.jpg\" width=\"364\" height=\"260\" /></p>       (DJ) KARENGERA KIRENGA  ERIC SOUL <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cwYrpHy.jpg\" width=\"385\" height=\"256\" />    MUTONI ANGEL  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tiUsbCH.jpg\" width=\"326\" height=\"217\" />MAZIMPAKA  PRIME Iri serukiramuco uretse itsinda rya ComponentsRw ryaryitabiriye,<br /> ryitabiriwe kandi nabandi bahanzi<br /> bakomeye barimo itsinda rya Umoja Boys ryo mu<br /> Buholandi,Slyvester &amp; Abramz, bo muri Uganda,<br /> Maurice Kirya ,Makadem wo muri Kenya, Coopy<br /> Bly, Cindy Sanyu, Berita wo muri Afurika y’Epfo,<br /> Feridah Rose, Jose Chameleone ,Bobi Wine,ndetse nabandi benshi batandukanye.<p>Iri tsinda rya ComponentsRw ryaherukaga mu gihugu cya Uganda muri<br /> Gicurasi mu iserukiramuco ryiswe Doadoa Festival, iri tsinda kandi<br /> ryanitabiriye umuhuro w\'abahanzi bo muri Afurika witwa Ongea wabereye<br /> muri Kenya mu kwezi kwa Werurwe uyu mwaka.</p>', 'itsinda ComponentsRw ryaserukiye u Rwanda muri Bayimba Festival bati \"Duhagaze bwuma', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'music-is-passion', '', '', '2017-12-03 15:46:44', '2017-12-03 15:46:44', '', 0, 'http://demo.themegrill.com/colormag/?p=117', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(123, 1, '2015-03-24 07:57:31', '2015-03-24 07:57:31', '<b>Rugamba Dorcy yavutse kuwa 29 Nzeri 1969,ni umuhanzi, umusizi akaba n’umukinnyi ndetse n\'uwanditsi w’amateyatere.</b>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Rugamba Dorcy yavutse kuwa 29 Nzeri 1969,ni\r\numuhanzi, umusizi akaba n’umukinnyi ndetse n\'uwanditsi w’amateyatere. Se umubyara\r\nni umuhanzi Rugamba Cyprien naho nyina akaba Daphrose Rugamba. Ni\r\numwana wa kabiri (ubuheta) mu muryango w’abana icumi. Rugamba akaba avuga indimi enye adategwa arizo ikinyarwanda,Igifaransa,<wbr />Icyongereza,Igiswahili.\r\nN’ubwo atari umuririmbyi nka se, Dorcy RUGAMBA ni umwe mu banyarwanda bake bagize ibikorwa by’umuco nk’umwuga. Impano yo kubikunda akaba\r\nyarabikuye kuri se wari umusizi n’umushakashatsi w’intyoza, Rugamba Cyprien</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SMfo7hB.jpg\" width=\"347\" height=\"347\" /></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Rugamba Cyprien na Daphrose Rugamba</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Aha tugiye kubanyuriramo amwe mu mateka ya Rugamba Dorcy mu bice\r\nbibiri bitandukanye aribyo :ubuzima bwe bwo hambere ndetse n\'ubuzima\r\nbwe bwo hanze y\'u Rwanda.Ubuzima bwe bwo hambereMuri 1976, Rugamba Dorcy yinjiye mu itorero Amasimbi n’Amakombe , afite imyaka 7 gusa.\r\nHagati aho yize amashuri abanza muri Ecole Belge de Butare, akomereza muri\r\nSeminari nto ya Karubanda (PS Virgo Fidelis); ngo icyo yakundaga cyane mu\r\nMasimbi n’Amakombe ni ukwiyerekakw’intore.\r\nYagiye muri tournée bwa mbere mu mwaka wa 1991, hari muri Suisse na Belgique. Nyuma yaje gukunda cyane ibi bikorwa ndangamuco, cyane cyaneubuvanganzo nyemvugo nk’ubusizi.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uSiHAD2.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Rugamba Dorcy</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Ibi bihe byiza rero byaje kurangizwa na Jenoside yakorewe Abatutsi yo muri Mata 1994. Iki gihe akaba yarigaga muri</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Kaminuza Nkuru y’u Rwanda mu ishami rya Pharmacie. Iri sanganya ryamutwaye ababyeyi na batandatu mu bavandimwe be, hari tariki 7/Mata/1994. Ubuzima bwe hanze y’u Rwanda</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SLx5CRc.jpg\" width=\"360\" height=\"241\" /></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Rugamba Dorcy</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Rugamba Dorcy arikumwe n’abavandimwe be babiri, bahisebajya i Burundi, bahava bajya i Paris.\r\nNyuma yageze mu Bubiligi aho yatangiye gukorana na groupe yo muri diaspora yitwa Amarebe n’Imena. Yatangiye no gukoresha inyandiko n’ibihangano byase wari utangiye gufatwa nk’icyatwa(monument national) mu Rwanda ahoabantu kugeza n’ubu bagikunda indirimbo ze. Rugamba Dorcy yakoranye n’umuryango witwa Groupov umukino (pièce) wiswe\r\nRwanda 94 ukaba umara amasaha 6 yose kuwukina</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZwdbS4Q.jpg\" width=\"355\" height=\"238\" /></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div align=\"left\">Mu rwego rwo kwihugura, yize muri  Conservatoire de Liège ariko anitabira ibirori bitandukanye nka Fest Africa 2000, aho bamutumiye kuza gukina mu\r\nRwanda muri 2004. Ahageze yahahuriye n’urubyiruko rukunda gukina ikinamico biyemeza gufatanya kugirango babashe kuba abakinnyi b’umwuga (comediens professionnels). Ni muri urwo rwego\r\nyashinze itorero ‘Urwintore’. Muri 2007 yatangiye gukina umukino(piece) wiswe\r\nL’instruction akora tournée mu bihugu byinshi byo ku isi. Iyi tournée\r\nyarakunzwe ku buryo ahantu nko mu murwa mukuru w\'igihugu cy\'Ubwongereza London ama salles yarakubitaga akuzura.\r\nDorcy Rugamba yatangarije ikinyamakuru IKAZE mu mwaka wa 2008\r\nko ikintu kimushimisha mu buzima ari ukuba atunzwe n’ubuhanzi bwe ; kuri we ngo ni nk’inzozi yakabije. Bamubajije inzozi afite ubu arasubiza ati”ni Leta\r\nZunze ubumwe za Afurika.” Abajijwe umuntu wamugiriye akamaro mu buzima bwe, yavuze ko ari se Cyprien Rugamba. Ikindi ngo we ukwemera kwe gushingiye\r\nku buzima bwo ku isi bwonyine kuko atemera ijuru; ati “nta dini ndimo.”</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rBb2Pvc.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"267\" /></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"> Daphrose Rugamba na Rugamba Cyprien</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Kuri ubu Rugamba Dorcy afite imishinga myinshi itandukanye igamije\r\nguteza imbere ubuhanzi,ikindi kandi ubu ni umuyobozi\r\nw\'ubuhanzi(Directeur Artistique) mu kigo Rwanda Arts Initiative(RAI).</div>', 'Amwe mu mateka y\'umuhanzi Rugamba Dorcy, umuhungu wa nyakwigendera Rugamba Sipiriyani.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'destruction-in-montania', '', '', '2017-12-04 08:31:50', '2017-12-04 08:31:50', '', 0, 'http://demo.themegrill.com/colormag/?p=123', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(129, 1, '2015-03-24 09:39:31', '2015-03-24 09:39:31', '<b>umuhanzi akaba intore Jabastar yamamaye cyane mundirimbo zivuga ibingwi by\'uRwanda akomeje gukora umuziki gakondo ufite umwihariko,Jabastar akaba yarahoze ari kapiteni w\'itorero ry\'igihugu Urukerereza.</b>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Umuhanzi Semanza Jean Baptiste uyu yamenyekanye cyane nka Jabastar ubusanzwe  n\'umwe mu bahanzi b\'abahanga mu njyana gakondo y\'abanyarwanda.\r\nuyu Jabastar yamamaye cyane mu mbyino gakondo aho ari umwe mu nkingi za mwamba mu itorero ry\'igihugu Urukerereza by\'umwihariko akaba anakora umuziki gakondo ku giti cye. Semanza Jean Baptiste[ Jabastar]akomeje gukora indirimbo zikoranye ubuhanga zitaka u Rwanda. Semanza yakoze indirimbo zagiye zimenyekana aha twavuga nka \'\'Abashyitsi\" nizindi nyinshi.Mu kiganiro  Intore Jabastar yagiranye na ikinyamakuru cy\'umuco umucowacu.com yatubwiye ko we aho akura inganzo ntahandi aruko agendera ku mateka n\'umwihariko w\'abanyarwanda. Uyu muhanzi akaba yamaze gushyira hanze indirimbo nshya, tumubajije uko yagize inganzo yiyi ndirimbo nshya yise \'\'U RWANDA RURAGENDWA\'\'.\r\nyadutangarije ko we nka Jabastar yishimiye urwego agezeho ati\" Nahimbye iyi ndirimbo nshaka kubwira abantu bari mu   Rwanda ,abari hanze ko u Rwanda ari igihugu kigendwa ,ngaruka k\'umahoro, umutekano biri iwacu i Rwanda,ikindi buri muntu wese ku isi akwiye kumenya ko u Rwanda rugendwa .\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/irrf7QW.jpg\" width=\"391\" height=\"490\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">indirimbo  \'\'U RWANDA RURAGENDWA\'\'. yamaze kugera kuri youtube aho wayireba ukaryoherwa na muziki y\'umwimerere</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">KANDA HANO UYUMVE:https:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E8tmHokRpoQ\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E8tmHokRpoQ</a></div>', 'Intore Jabastar afatanyije na N PAZZ0 bamaze gushyira hanze indirimbo \'\'U RWANDA RURAGENDWA\'\'.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'get-more-nutrition-in-every-bite', '', '', '2017-12-09 12:25:35', '2017-12-09 12:25:35', '', 0, 'http://demo.themegrill.com/colormag/?p=129', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(132, 1, '2015-03-24 09:43:30', '2015-03-24 09:43:30', '<b>Itorero Inkindi Itatse rikorera mu kigo cyo kwa Gisimba mu Nyakabanda bishimiye bikomeye gukorana na Mani Martin ndetse na Eddy Kenzo nk\'abahanzi b\'abahanga kandi bamaze kumenyekana muri Afurika y\'uburasirazuba ndetse nahandi henshi hatandukanye.</b>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Mu kiganiro ikinyamakuru Umuco Wacu cyagiranye na Hitimana Constantin\r\numuyobozi w\'itorero inkindi itatse yatangiye agira ati &lt;&lt; Twishimiye\r\ncyane gukorana na Mani Martin kandi iyi ni intambwe nziza, ubundi\r\ntwamenyanye na Mani Martin mu mushinga nanone w\'indirimbo yitwa\r\nNdaraye turi gupanga nayo gukora gusa twabaye duhereye kuri Afro\r\nisubiyemo(Afro Remix),yakunze cyane imibyinire yacu ikindi kandi Mani\r\nMartin si Umuhanzi upfa gukorana na abantu babonetse bose kuba\r\nyaraduhisemo tugakorana ni intambwe ikomeye...&gt;&gt;</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jGnVCSm.jpg\" width=\"390\" height=\"188\" />\r\n\r\nItorero Inkindi Itatse ni itorero gakondo ryatangiye mu mwaka  2013,\r\nni ukuvuga ko rimaze imyaka ine yonyine. Kubw\'ibyo rero abagize iri\r\ntorero bahamya ko gukorana n\'abahanzi nka Mani Martin ndetse na Eddy\r\nKenzo umuhanzi rurangiranwa ukomoka mu gihugu cy\'ubugande  ari ntambwe\r\nnziza bateye ibaganisha ku ntsinzi.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gBF4SiP.jpg\" width=\"394\" height=\"394\" />\r\nNdagira ngo mbibutse ko indirimbo Afro itorero inkindi itatse\r\nrizagaragaramo ari Afro isubiwemo(Afro Remix) umuhanzi nyarwanda Mani\r\nMartin yasubiranyemo na Eddy Kenzo umuhanzi ukomoka mu gihugu\r\ncy\'ubugande, bikaba binateganyijwe ko amashusho yiyi ndirimbo azajya\r\nhanze bidatinze.</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><i><b>REBA AMAFOTO:</b></i></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><i><b><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IVzSslc.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"249\" /></b></i></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2VOrx7F.jpg\" width=\"335\" height=\"223\" /></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NGGzdNB.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"232\" /></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/S4ANEqF.jpg\" width=\"431\" height=\"288\" /></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NLr0XOh.jpg\" width=\"341\" height=\"227\" /></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/P2ZTm4F.jpg\" width=\"337\" height=\"224\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5wVcw8J.jpg\" width=\"366\" height=\"221\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FpxwgQy.jpg\" width=\"395\" height=\"267\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FM8yYmu.jpg\" width=\"388\" height=\"481\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jQS9Ffr.jpg\" width=\"370\" height=\"256\" />\r\n\r\n</div>', 'itorero Inkindi Itatse bishimiye bikomeye gukorana na Mani Martin ndetse na Eddy Kenzo muri Afro Remix/AMAFOTO', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'solar-eclipse-eye-health-warning', '', '', '2017-12-09 12:23:47', '2017-12-09 12:23:47', '', 0, 'http://demo.themegrill.com/colormag/?p=132', 0, 'post', '', 0);
