(311, 1, '2017-10-22 14:57:23', '2017-10-22 14:57:23', '<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-303\" src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/post-209x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"441\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\n<b><strong>Poetic Fever ni igitaramo ngarukakwezi gitegurwa n\'itsinda Transpoesis. Igitaramo Poetic Fever cy\'uku kwezi k\'Ukwakira cyabaye kuri uyu wa gatandatu tariki ya 14/ Ukwakira 2017 kibera i Kigali muri Blue Note.</strong></b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIki gitaramo cyari akataraboneka, ni igitaramo cyari kitabiriwe n\'abasizi batandukanye bakomeye hano mu Rwanda ndetse no mu karere k\'Afurika y\'uburasirazuba(East Africa).\r\n\r\nIki gitaramo cyatangiye ahagana ku i saa mbili z\'umugoroba maze Kivumbi King abimburira abandi basizi kuri uwo mugoroba nuko atarama mu gisigo cye yise \"Questions\" tushyize mu kinyarwanda bisobanuye \"Ibibazo\",Kivumbi yaje gukurikirwa na isamiejr(Ruhindi Sam) nawe atarama mu gisigo yise \"Hear my cry mama nation tugenekereje mu kinyarwanda bivuze ngo \"Ndumva amarira y\'igihugu cyambyaye\", nyuma ya Sam ku rubyiniro haje kabuhariwe Maniraguha carine maze injyana arayipima mu tubangutso n\'utubeshuro aterura umuvugo yise \"Isi ya none\" ,abaraho ibyishimo bibasaba ku masura, Maniraguha yakurikiwe na kabuhariwe Eric Onyango Otienno (Rix poet) umusizi ukomoka mu gihugu cya Kenya akaba ari nawe wari umutumirwa mukuru w\'icyo gitaramo maze atarama mu muvugo yise woman cg umugore mu rurimi rw\'ikinyarwanda, uyu yakurikiwe na Fefe Kalume atarama mu muvugo we yise \"La mort d\'une mere\" bisobanuye \"Urupfu rw\' umubyeyi w\'umugore\", bigeze aho ,igitaramo cyasaga nkikimaze kuryoha maze kiryoha kurushaho aho Akeem Marvin na\r\n\r\numusizi ufite ubumuga bwo kutabona bageraga ku rubyiniro bagafatanya mu muvugo bise \"Only you\" cg \"Wowe gusa\". Uyu muvugo waba bombi wari wiganjemo imitoma, Anesie yagumye ku rubyiniro maze mu ijwi ryiza rizira amakaraza yigana nyakwigendera Kamariza mu ndirimbo \"Maragahinda\" maze abari aho ibyishimo birabasaba, amarangamutima ababana menshi batangarira uburyo uwo musizi ufite ubumuga bwo kutabona yigana Kamariza bya nyabyo.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIki gitaramo cyagaragayemo imivugo n\'ibisigo bihimbitse mu buryo bwa gihanga, iki gitaramo cyasusurukijwe kandi na Bahati Innocent yifashishije umuvugo we yise \"Mwana wa Mabukwe\" nindi myinshi myiza. Abasizi bagiye basimburanywa mu buryo butandukanye gusa icyanga gikomeza kuba cyakindi bashimangira ko mu busizi harimo icyanga.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nMu kiganiro ikinyamakuru Umuco wacu cyagiranye na madamu Dr Andrea Grieder umuyobozi wa Transpoesis itsinda ritegura icyo gitaramo yatangiye agira ati \" Nukuri ndishimye bitavugwa, nabonye abasizi bakataraboneka ku rubyiniro ikindi kandi iyi gahunda yo kuvangavanga imivugo n\'ibicurangisho by\'umuziki ni byiza cyane nabonye bikora ku mitima na roho by\'abafana, ikindi navuga Transpoesis ifite imishinga myinshi ku busizi nka Kigali itatswe n\'ubusizi ndetse niyi Poetic Fever bityo rero mboneyeho gutumira abantu muri rusange ngo baze twiyumvire icyanga cy\'ubusizi\"\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_304\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"300\"]<img class=\"wp-image-304 size-medium\" src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/pDGAbMN-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /> Dr Andrea Grieder[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_305\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img class=\"wp-image-305 size-medium\" src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/fkbmbWV-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /> ISamie Jr[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_306\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"300\"]<img class=\"wp-image-306 size-medium\" src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/cBmQdF2-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /> Maniraguha[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"atta