(364, 2, '2017-12-01 21:19:45', '2017-12-01 21:19:45', '<b><strong>Ashimwe Ange Theonastine ni umusizi mu rurimi rw\'icyongereza,yabonye izuba tariki ya 30 Gicurasi 1999,avukira mu ntara y\'amajyaruguru, Ashimwe ni mwene Tugengwenayo Theonas na Kantarama Marie Claire batuye mu karere ka Musanze,intara y\'amajyaruguru.</strong></b>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Umusizi Ashimwe Ange nubwo kuri ubu abana n\'ubumuga bw\'ingingo ngo siko byahoze! Abajijwe uko byaje yasubije muri aya magambo</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\" Icyambere navutse nk\'abandi bana bose,gusa mfite imyaka itandatu kugenda byatagiye kwanga, ikibazo narimfite n\'imbaraga nke mu maguru, naho ibya Scoliosis(inyonjo) byatewe no kwicara igihe kinini kuko ntabashaga  guhagarara. Bamwe bavuga ko bandoze gusa bamwe barabyemeza abandi bakabihakana, njye ntana kimwe mbiziho,mu rugo bamvuje ahashoboka hose haba mu Rwanda ndetse no hanze, gusa nabonye byanze ndiyakira ubundi ndiyigira. Ubumuga bwanjye bwatangiye kuva ubwo, ubu mfite imyaka 18 bivuzeko uyu mwaka ari uwa 12 ntagenda.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">                    Umusizi Ashimwe Ange</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hanyuma Ashimwe Ange abajijwe uko ibyo kuba umusizi byaje yasubije agira ati</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \"Nyine nize amashuri abanza ntabana n\'ababyeyi... noneho umukozi twabanaga yarankubitaga bikaze nuko yankubita nkanga kurira nkajya kwicara inyuma ya Doro nkarira ,nasoza kurira nkasoma ibitabo kuko mu mwaka wanjye wa mbere mu mashuri abanza narinzi gusoma ikinyarwanda neza cyane.... Iyo nasomaga igitabo nkakirangiza nandikaga ahantu... Mu wa mbere naharangije maze gusoma ibitabo bya Edition Bakame 17. Narangije amashuri abanza maze gusoma nk\'ibitabo bigera kuri 70 kuko uko umuntu yambwiraga nabi nasomaga igitabo aho kumusubiza.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Uko nakuze nkunda gusoma niko naje gukunda kwandika nkumva nanjye nakwandika....Iyo nashakaga igitabo cyo gusoma nkakibura Numvaga nakwandika icyanjye...Ngeze mu mashuri y\'icyiciro rusange(Tronc Commun) nandikaga inkuru z\'uruhererekane mu ikayi, gusoma igice kimwe(chapter)abanyeshuri bakampa 300frw... Ndi mu mwaka wa 4 mu mashuri yisumbuye ubwo twari mu bizamini nasoje gukora kare ntangira kwibaza niba nzibukwa... Ndabyandika ku rupapuro rw\'ibibazo ,nuko nsohotse umuntu arusomye arambaza ngo\" uzi umusizi witwa Angel Uwamahoro? Ndamubwira ngo oya, ahita ambwira ngo mwandika kimwe, ufite impano y\'ubusizi nuko utabizi..... nguko uko natangjye kubikunda no kubikora.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">                                  Umusizi Ashimwe Ange</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ashimwe Ange Theonastine kuri ubu ni umunyeshuri mu mwaka wa gatanu w\'amashuri yisumbuye mu ishami ry\'amateka,ubukungu n\'ubumenyi bw\'isi.(HEG) mu ishuri ryisumbuye rya Cyabingo mu ntara y\'amajyaruguru mu karere ka Musanze.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ashimwe Ange Theonastine n\'umwe mu begukanye irushanwa ry\'ubusizi rikomeye hano mu Rwanda ariryo Kigali Itatswe n\'Ubusizi,aho yahembwe ibihembo byinshi bitandukanye harimo n\'ishusho ya Nyiraruganzu Nyirarumaga, nyirakuruza w\'ubusizi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ikindi kandi Ashimwe Ange Theonastine yizeye kuzakira nkuko abivuga muri aya magambo ati \"Nizeye kuzakira,naho bitabaho nkiri muri ubu buzima na nyuma yabwo nzakira.\"</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ange kandi yavuze icyo ubusizi aricyo kuri we muri aya magambo ati \"Ubusizi ni ubuzima bwanjye, ndabucyeneye kugira mbeho bityo mbamyako kuri njye Ubusizi ni igisobanuro cy\'ubuzima.\"</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">                              Umusizi Ashimwe Ange</p>', 'Ubuzima bwa Ashimwe Ange Theonastine,umusizi ubana n\'ubumuga.', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '359-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-12-01 21:19:45', '2017-12-01 21:19:45', '', 359, 'http://new.umucowacu.com/2017/12/01/359-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(365, 2, '2017-12-01 21:27:04', '2017-12-01 21:27:04', '<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Muri uyu muvugo ucuranze ukaba unahimbitse mu buryo bwa gihanga,Umusizi Tuyisenge aba yibaza byinshi ku myambarire n\'imitekerereze yo muri iyi minsi! Imwe mu mirongo igize uyu muvugo twavuga ni nkaho agera akibaza ati \"Ese Gihanga umuhanga ko yasize igihango,aho yagaruka agasanga ibyo yasize dusenga byarimukiye mu gusirimba,gusakuza biheruka burya? Ese yabikirwa ni iki? Na odeur ya ocean?cyangwa nawe batwikira ikoma bagashyira ku karubanda ubwambure bw\'umwami? Babikora nta dini batunga!\".</p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Uyu n\'umwe mu mivugo uyu muhungu asa naho yakoze atishimiye uko imyambarire y\'ubu imeze. Muri uyu muvugo Umusizi Tuyisenge yumvikana anenga byeruye umuhanzikazi Odda Paccy usa nkaho ariwe wazanye iriya nkubiri yo kwambara ikoma.</p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mu kiganiro ikinyamakuru Umuco wacu cyagiranye na Tuyisenge Olivier yatangiye agira ati \" Kwambara ubushwange aho ni umuco? cyangwa ni ubushwi bukuzwa bugakwirakwizwa? Ayo nayo n\'amwe mu magambo ari mu muvugo wanjye gusa icyo nifuza kuvuga n\'ukubwira abanyarwanda n\'abanyarwandakazi ko u Rwanda rugira umuco,kwambara amakoma ubundi ni igitutsi kibi,biriya si ibintu bikwiye umwali cyangwa umusore w\'i Rwanda, biba ngombwa ko umuntu akosora mugenzi nubwo ababikoze bose yenda ari bakuru kuri njye, ibuye ryahanuye inyoni bitangana.</p><p> </p><p>                                                                             <img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/TUYI-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Umusizi akomeza atangariza Umuco wacu ko atakoze uyu muvugo mu rwego rwo kwibasira ababikoze kuko we ahamya ko ntan\'umwe baziranye byimbitse. Ikindi kandi akomeza asaba urubyiruko kutiruka inyuma y\'ibiguruka byose.</p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Uyu muvugo ukaba warakozwe n\'umuryango Iwacu in Africa biciye muri situdiyo Rwanda image Films. Iwacu in Africa ni umuryango wamaze gusinyisha abasizi icyenda b\'abanyarwanda mu rwego rwo kubafasha mu iterambere ry\'ibihangano byabo. Umusizi Tuyisenge aratangaza ko bidatinze n\'amashusho y\'uyu muvugo azaba kuba ugeze hanze.</p><p>KANDA HANO <a href=\"https://youtu.be/uaMkjwV8Ayo\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uaMkjwV8Ayo</a></p>', 'Umusizi Tuyisenge yamaze gushyira hanze umuvugo yise \"Niba ari ibyo nta Rwanda\"', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'umusizi-tuyisenge-yamaze-gushyira-hanze-umuvugo-yise-niba-ari-ibyo-nta-rwanda', '', '', '2017-12-01 21:46:36', '2017-12-01 21:46:36', '', 0, 'http://new.umucowacu.com/?p=365', 0, 'post', '', 0),
