(379, 2, '2017-12-01 21:57:48', '2017-12-01 21:57:48', '<b><strong>Sengabo Jodas ni umuririmbyi mu njyana gakondo ukomoka mu Bwiza bwa Mukarange hakaba mu karere ka Kayonza mu burasirazuba bw\'u Rwanda. </strong></b>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Sengabo Jodas ni mwene Gashema ka Sengabo Rusa Daniel wamamaye cyane mu Buganza mu myaka yo hambere kubera gukunda inka cyane,inka yatumye amenyekana cyane niyo yise Rwamunihiri kuko yarayitonesheje bishira kera ndetse Sengabo Rusa uwo akaba yari inshuti y\'inkoramutima n\'umwami w\'u Rwanda Mutara wa gatatu Rudahigwa.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sengabo Jodas amaze kugira indirimbo zigera ku munani gusa yamenyekanye cyane mu ndirimbo yise\" Bene u Rwanda\". aho aba avuga ibigwi u Rwanda nk\'igihugu cyamubyaye.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kuri ubu uyu muhanzi yamaze gushyira hanze indirimbo ye nshya yise \"Akanyange\" yatuye umukunzi we ahamya ko akunda byabuze urugero.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Iyi ndirimbo ni indirimbo yiganjemo imitoma no gutetesha. Mu kiganiro Sengabo yagiranye n\'ikinyamakuru Umuco wacu yatangiye agira ati \" Indirimbo Akanyange ni indirimbo nkunda, ni indirimbo nahimbiye umukobwa, Akanyange ni igisingizo nahaye umukobwa,nahimbye iyi ndirimbo kugira nerekane uko urukundo nyarwo rwakagombye kuba rumeze\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Uyu muhanzi Sengabo akaba ari umwe mubazi neza kwigana imiririmbire y\'umuhanzikazi Cecile Kayirebwa dore Sengabo yari mu bahanzi baririmbanye na Cecile Kayirebwa mu gitaramo cyo kwizihiza isabukuru y\'imyaka mirongo irindwi ya Kayirebwa.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ikindi kandi Sengabo akaba yarakuriye mu itorero Indangamirwa ry\'Inyamirambo akaba ari naho akiririmba.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Indirimbo Akanyange ikaba yarageze hanze muri iki cyumweru turimo. Sengabo akaba akomeje gukora cyane ndetse akaba afite gahunda yo kuzamura urwego rwe ndetse akanakorana n\'abandi bahanzi.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nUMVA 