(397, 2, '2017-12-02 10:49:42', '2017-12-02 10:49:42', '<b><strong>Kaci kaci Art Festival ni iserukiramuco rigiye kuba ku ncuro yaryo ya mbere,rikazabera mu mujyi wa Musanze ku wa 11/Ugushyingo/2017 ahitwa ku Nshuti art and culture center hateganye na Banki ya Kigali ishami rya Musanze.</strong></b>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Iri serukiramuco rizaba ryiganjemo ibikorwa byinshi bitandukanye by\'ubuhanzi,ubukorikori n\'ubugeni,hazagaragaramo gushushanya abantu ku masura(face painting), kwigishwa kuboha, iri serukiramuco si umuziki n\'ubugeni gusa hazanabaho gusogongera ku binyobwa byo hambere birimo Ikigage,urwagwa nibindi byinshi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Muri iri serukiramuco hazanagaramo bimwe mu bikorwa byo hambere bitagikorwa aha twavuga nko kurasa intego,gucana umuriro w\'urushingo ndetse n\'imbyino zo hambere zarangaga abantu bo mu majyaruguru cyane cyane i Musanze.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Iri serukiramuco rikaba rizitababirwa na bamwe mu bahanzi bakomeye hano iwacu mu Rwanda, aha twavuga nka Mani Martin umuhanzi umaze kugira ibikorwa by\'indashyikirwa mu buhanzi bwe.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_399\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/CNx8JOF-300x228.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"228\" /> Mani Martin[/caption]\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Undi muhanzi uzitabira iri Serukiramuco ni Patrick Nyamitali,umwe mu bahanzi b\'abahanga ukora mu muhogo akibutsa benshi muzika yo hambere kubw\'ijwi rye rizira amakaraza.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_400\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/WuNmWDT-300x199.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" /> Patrick Nyamitali[/caption]\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Undi muhanzi uzitabira iri serukiramuco ni Rwamwiza baratari imihigo Sentore Jules kabuhariwe mu njyana gakondo y\'abanyarwanda.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_401\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/oZ4EkSS-300x199.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" /> Sentore Jules[/caption]\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Abandi twavuga bazitabira Kaci Kaci Art Festival harimo Andy Bumuntu,Peace Jolis ndetse n\'abakunzi b\'ubusizi ntibabibagiwe kuko bazataramirwa na kizigenza Ngangare Eric(Eric onekey). Iri serukiramuco rizasusurutswa n\'amatorero atatu gakondo yo mu mujyi wa Musanze ndetse n\'itsinda Yemba Voice ryo ku ishuri rya muzika ryo ku Nyundo hanyuma umushyushyarugamba w\'iri serukiramuco akazaba ari Karengera Kirenga Eric Soul umuhungu wa Cecile Kayirebwa.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_402\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/QWTOY7t-300x298.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"298\" /> Eric(Eric onekey)[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_384\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/yYmTS9O-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" /> Yemba Voice[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_403\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/NL2qFqA-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" /> Peace Jolis[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_404\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/YHKrNcK-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /> Eric Soul[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_405\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/B1kIThA-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" /> Andy Bumuntu[/caption]\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kaci Kaci Art Festival ni iserukiramuco riri gutegurwa n\'abantu batatu aribo Mutuyimana Ella Liliane, Sibomana Alexandre ndetse na Habyarima Jean Luc bari bamenyerewe cyane mu ruganda rwa cinema.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_406\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"281\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/IMG-20171027-WA0001-281x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"281\" height=\"300\" /> Mutuyimana Ella Liliane[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_407\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"247\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/GCk815h-247x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"247\" height=\"300\" /> Habyarima Jean Luc[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_408\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"231\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/kjckthk.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"231\" height=\"231\" /> Sibomana Alexandre[/caption]\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mu kiganiro ikinyamakuru Umuco Wacu cyagiranye na Mutuyimana Ella Liliane umwe mubari gutegura iri serukiramuco akaba yatangiye agira ati\" Kaci Kaci igiye kuba ku nshuro ya mbere,twahisemo umujyi wa Musanze kuko ibitaramo hafi ya byose bibera i Kigali,twasanze hari abantu baba mu ntara baba bakeneye kwishima ndetse no kumenya umuco nyarwanda ,bakanamenya n\'abahanzi babo, ikindi nuko abazaza bahishiwe byinshi birimo kuzibutswa byinshi mubyarangaga abanyarwanda bo hambere...\"</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kaci Kaci Art Festival izaba ku wa gatandatu tariki ya 11/Ugushyingo/2017 i Musanze guhera i saa yine z\'amanywa kugeza i saa tanu z\'ijoro hanyuma kwinjira ni amafaranga igihumbi (1000Rwf) ahasanzwe ndetse n\'ibihumbi bitatu(3000rwf) mu cyubahiro.</p>\r\n<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/IMG-20171027-WA0003-240x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"300\" />', 'Musanze hagiye kubera iserukiramuco ry\'akataboneka ryiswe \"Kaci kaci Art Festival\".', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'musanze-hagiye-kubera-iserukiramuco-ryakataboneka-ryiswe-kaci-kaci-art-festival', '', '', '2017-12-09 12:45:49', '2017-12-09 12:45:49', '', 0, 'http://new.umucowacu.com/?p=397', 0, 'post', '', 0),
