(409, 2, '2017-12-02 10:49:25', '2017-12-02 10:49:25', '<p><b><strong>Kaci kaci Art Festival ni iserukiramuco rigiye kuba ku ncuro yaryo ya mbere,rikazabera mu mujyi wa Musanze ku wa 11/Ugushyingo/2017 ahitwa ku Nshuti art and culture center hateganye na Banki ya Kigali ishami rya Musanze.</strong></b></p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Iri serukiramuco rizaba ryiganjemo ibikorwa byinshi bitandukanye by\'ubuhanzi,ubukorikori n\'ubugeni,hazagaragaramo gushushanya abantu ku masura(face painting), kwigishwa kuboha, iri serukiramuco si umuziki n\'ubugeni gusa hazanabaho gusogongera ku binyobwa byo hambere birimo Ikigage,urwagwa nibindi byinshi.</p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Muri iri serukiramuco hazanagaramo bimwe mu bikorwa byo hambere bitagikorwa aha twavuga nko kurasa intego,gucana umuriro w\'urushingo ndetse n\'imbyino zo hambere zarangaga abantu bo mu majyaruguru cyane cyane i Musanze.</p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Iri serukiramuco rikaba rizitababirwa na bamwe mu bahanzi bakomeye hano iwacu mu Rwanda, aha twavuga nka Mani Martin umuhanzi umaze kugira ibikorwa by\'indashyikirwa mu buhanzi bwe.</p>[caption id=\"attachment_399\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/CNx8JOF-300x228.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"228\" /> Mani Martin[/caption]<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Undi muhanzi uzitabira iri Serukiramuco ni Patrick Nyamitali,umwe mu bahanzi b\'abahanga ukora mu muhogo akibutsa benshi muzika yo hambere kubw\'ijwi rye rizira amakaraza.</p>[caption id=\"attachment_400\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/WuNmWDT-300x199.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" /> Patrick Nyamitali[/caption]<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Undi muhanzi uzitabira iri serukiramuco ni Rwamwiza baratari imihigo Sentore Jules kabuhariwe mu njyana gakondo y\'abanyarwanda.</p>[caption id=\"attachment_401\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img src=\"http://umuc