s/2017/12/IMG-20171027-WA0001-281x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"281\" height=\"300\" /> Mutuyimana Ella Liliane[/caption][caption id=\"attachment_407\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"247\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/GCk815h-247x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"247\" height=\"300\" /> Habyarima Jean Luc[/caption][caption id=\"attachment_408\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"231\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/kjckthk.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"231\" height=\"231\" /> Sibomana Alexandre[/caption]<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mu kiganiro ikinyamakuru Umuco Wacu cyagiranye na Mutuyimana Ella Liliane umwe mubari gutegura iri serukiramuco akaba yatangiye agira ati\" Kaci Kaci igiye kuba ku nshuro ya mbere,twahisemo umujyi wa Musanze kuko ibitaramo hafi ya byose bibera i Kigali,twasanze hari abantu baba mu ntara baba bakeneye kwishima ndetse no kumenya umuco nyarwanda ,bakanamenya n\'abahanzi babo, ikindi nuko abazaza bahishiwe byinshi birimo kuzibutswa byinshi mubyarangaga abanyarwanda bo hambere...\"</p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kaci Kaci Art Festival izaba ku wa gatandatu tariki ya 11/Ugushyingo/2017 i Musanze guhera i saa yine z\'amanywa kugeza i saa tanu z\'ijoro hanyuma kwinjira ni amafaranga igihumbi (1000Rwf) ahasanzwe ndetse n\'ibihumbi bitatu(3000rwf) mu cyubahiro.</p><p><img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/IMG-20171027-WA0003-240x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"300\" /></p>', 'Musanze hagiye kubera iserukiramuco ry\'akataboneka ryiswe \"Kaci kaci Art Festival\".', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '397-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-02 10:49:25', '2017-12-02 10:49:25', '', 397, 'http://new.umucowacu.com/2017/12/02/397-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
