zi bazasusurutsa abazitabira Poetic Fever harimo Fefe Karume umuhanga mu busizi mu rurimi rw\'Igifaransa, Sam Ruhindi(ISamiejr) umwe mu basizi b\'abahanga kandi bafite umwihariko mu busizi mu rurimi rw\'icyongereza, Akeem Marvin nawe n\'umwe muri bakabuhariwe mu busizi bw\'Icyongereza,atondeka imirongo ugatwarwa ukananirwa kwihishira ukabigaragaza.</p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">      </p>[caption id=\"attachment_417\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/IMG-20171009-WA0009-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> Fefe Karume[/caption]<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">  </p>[caption id=\"attachment_305\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/fkbmbWV-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /> Sam Ruhindi(ISamiejr)[/caption]<p><img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/IMG-20171009-WA0002-300x298.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"298\" /></p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Akeem Marvin  icyirango cy\'umuvugo yise ibaruwa kuri perezida wanjye yatuye Perezida Kagame</p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </p><p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Iki gitaramo kizitabirwa na kabuhariwe mu busizi ukomoka mu gihugu cya Kenya witwa Eric Onyango Otieno uzwi ku izina rya Rix Poet iwabo mu gihugu cya Kenya</p><p><img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/3QeA3Jm-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></p><p>Iki gitaramo kizaba ku wa gatandatu tariki 14/Ukwakira/2017 guhera i saa moya n\'igice z\'umugoroba(7:30pm) mu mujyi iruhande rwa Ecole Belge ahitwa Blue Note hanyuma kwinjira ni ibihumbi bitatu by\'amafaranga y\'u Rwanda(3000rwf) ku basanzwe ndetse n\'igihumbi(1000rwf) ku banyeshuri bafite ikarita y\'ishuri</p>', 'Ku nshuro ya kabiri Transpoesis iri gutegura igitaramo \"Poetic Fever\"', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '135-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-03 15:36:32', '2017-12-03 15:36:32', '', 135, 'http://new.umucowacu.com/2017/12/03/135-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
