(422, 2, '2017-12-03 15:45:17', '2017-12-03 15:45:17', '<b>Abagize itsinda ComponentsRw rigizwe n\' umuvangavangamiziki(Dj) Karengera Kirenga Eric Soul, umukirigitananga Munyakazi Deo, abaraperi babiri aribo Mazimpaka Prime na Angel Mutoni, guhera kuri uyu wa 22 Nzeri 2017 barabarizwa mu murwa mukuru w\'igihugu cy\'Ubugande Kampala aho bitabiriye iserukiramuco ryitwa Bayimba Festival.</b>\n<div align=\"left\">\nitsinda  ComponentsRw bahagurutse i Kigali mu gitondo cyo\nkuri uyu wa Gatanu berekeza mu gihugu cya Uganda ahagiye kubera iri\nserukiramuco rya Bayimba Festival rigiye kuba ku ncuro ya cumi, rikaba\nryitabiriwe n\'abahanzi baturutse mu bihugu bitandukanye ku isi. Iri\ntsinda rihagarariye u Rwanda biteganyijwe ko riri bususurutse\nabitabiriye iri serukiramuco uyu munsi tariki ya 23/ Nzeri 2017 guhera\ni saa tatu z\'ijoro ku isaha yo mu bugande n\'ukuvuga saa mbili z\'ijoro\nku isaha yo mu Rwanda.\n\nAba bahanzi baratangaza ko nyuma yo kugera Uganda amahoro bameze neza\nko biteguye kuza gutarama bagacyura inganji nkuko Munyakazi Deo umwe\nmu bahanzi bagize itsinda ComponentsRw yabitangarije ikinyamakuru\numucowacu.com Yatangiye agira ati \"Mukuri turiteguye cyane,twagerageje\ngukora imyitozo ihagije pee!! Ndagira ngo niba hari abanyarwanda bari\ninaha bakunda umuziki w\'umwimerere bazi kuza badushyigikire twe nka\nComponentsRw duhagaze bwuma\".</div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iynUhcb.jpg\" width=\"388\" height=\"388\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\">                              MUNYAKAZI DEO\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lg6gvIB.jpg\" width=\"364\" height=\"260\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\">       (DJ) KARENGERA KIRENGA  ERIC SOUL</div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cwYrpHy.jpg\" width=\"385\" height=\"256\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\">    MUTONI ANGEL</div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tiUsbCH.jpg\" width=\"326\" height=\"217\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\">MAZIMPAKA  PRIME</div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\">Iri serukiramuco uretse itsinda rya ComponentsRw ryaryitabiriye,\nryitabiriwe kandi nabandi bahanzi\nbakomeye barimo itsinda rya Umoja Boys ryo mu\nBuholandi,Slyvester &amp; Abramz, bo muri Uganda,\nMaurice Kirya ,Makadem wo muri Kenya, Coopy\nBly, Cindy Sanyu, Berita wo muri Afurika y’Epfo,\nFeridah Rose, Jose Chameleone ,Bobi Wine,ndetse nabandi benshi batandukanye.\n\nIri tsinda rya ComponentsRw ryaherukaga mu gihugu cya Uganda muri\nGicurasi mu iserukiramuco ryiswe Doadoa Festival, iri tsinda kandi\nryanitabiriye umuhuro w\'abahanzi bo muri Afurika witwa Ongea wabereye\nmuri Kenya mu kwezi kwa Werurwe uyu mwaka.</div>', 'itsinda ComponentsRw ryaserukiye u Rwanda muri Bayimba Festival bati \"Duhagaze bwuma', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '117-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-12-03 15:45:17', '2017-12-03 15:45:17', '', 117, 'http://new.umucowacu.com/2017/12/03/117-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
