gera ino natangiye kujya numva indirimbo za kera zicuranze mu nanga numva ndazikunze cyane,ndatekereza ko igihe kimwe nanjye nazakora indirimbo byibura yiganjemo umuco gakondo w\'abanyarwanda.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Uyu muhanzi kandi aherutse mu Rwanda mu byumweru bibiri bishize aho yari yakoranye igitaramo na bamwe mu bahanzi b\'abanyarwanda aha navuga nka Deo Munyakazi,Moise... iki gitaramo cyari cyabereye Roots house ku Kacyiru.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Makadeem yari yazanywe mu Rwanda n\'itsinda Afrogroov riyoborwa na Karengera Kirenga Eric Soul umuhungu wa Cecile Kayirebwa. Iri tsinda risanzwe ritegura ibitaramo gakondo rikanatumira bamwe mu bahanzi b\'ibyamamare ku migabane itandukanye y\'Isi. Mu bandi bahanzi iri tsinda ryazanye mu Rwanda twavuga nka Joss Stone umuririmbyikazi w\'umunyamerika akaba n\'umwe mu bafite kimwe mu bihembo bikomeye muri icyo gihugu aricyo Grammy award.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Uyu muhanzi Makadeem amaze kumenyekana mu bihugu byinshi bitandukanye ku isi kuko amaze kuzenguruka imigabane myinshi acuranga iki gicurangisho cya Nyatiti!! Bimwe mu bihugu Makadeem amaze gucurangiramo Nyatiti ni nka Poland,Crossia,Mexico,Ubudage. Uyu muhanzi abajijwe ku bavuga ko umuziki wa Kenya waba warateye imbere mu buryo bwa kinyamwuga kurusha uw\'abanyarwanda yasubije yisekera ati\" Burya iyo umuhanzi akora kandi akagira abamukurikira(followers)sinzi aho umuntu yahera avuga ngo si umunyamwuga, ahubwo uwo waba uhakana ibyo akora numva we yakora ibye akamurusha. Ibyo rero byuko Kenya ari abanyamwuga kurusha abanyarwanda simbizi.\"</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Makadeem ni umwe mu bahanzi gakondo baba nyafurika bamaze gutumirwa n\'ibinyamakuru bikomeye hano ku isi aha navuga nka BBC,NBC,.. Makadeem aratangaza kandi agiye gukora uko ashoboye isi yose ikamenya Nyatiti!</p>', 'Umuhanzi w\'icyamamare mu gihugu cya Kenya Makadeem ngo arifuza umunsi umwe kuzakora indirimbo yiganjyemo umuco nyarwanda.', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '139-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-09 12:17:45', '2017-12-09 12:17:45', '', 139, 'http://new.umucowacu.com/2017/12/09/139-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
