(444, 2, '2017-12-03 16:34:36', '2017-12-03 16:34:36', '<b>Inkera y\'inyamibwa ni igitaramo cyabaye mu ijoro ryo kuri uyu wa gatanu tariki ya 8 NZERI muri Kigali Serena Hotel kikaba cyahuje amatorero ndangamuco ya za kaminuza.</b>\n<div align=\"left\">Inkera y\'inyamibwa ni igitaramo kiba gikubiyemo amarushanwa ahuza\namatorero yaza kaminuza, iki gitaramo kikaba gitegurwa n\'umuryango\nwitwa Rwanda Culture Promoters Initiative umuryango w\'abanyeshuri\nb\'abanyarwanda bari muri za Kaminuza zitandukanye baharanira guteza imbere umuco.</div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bqr9KnB.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\">\nIki gitaramo cyatangiye ahagana mu ma saa moya z\'umugoroba maze\nkwikubitiro Winners Band aba ariyo isusurutsa abitabiriye iyi nkera\ny\'inyamibwa, hanyuma ikurikirwa na Bageni Hyacinthe umuhanzi gakondo\nucuranga iningiri,bidatinze abashyushyarugamba b\'iyi nkera aribo\nUmusizi Munezero Ferdinand na UWIMANA Honorine batangije amarushanwa ku\nmugaragaro maze itorero indahigwa rya IPRC ya Kigali ribanza ku\nrubyiniro rirabyina karahava,abahungu bagwa mu nka,bashiki babo\nbarashayaya bishyira kera.</div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jGWtlZo.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\nIndahigwa zaje gukurikirwa n\'itorero rya kaminuza ya</div>\n<div align=\"left\">African leadership University. maze nabo</div>\n<div align=\"left\">barabyina karahava ibirori biba ibirori koko.</div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qWbzjd5.jpg\" width=\"362\" height=\"241\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\">\n\nHanyuma  abagize itorero rya Kaminuza y\'u Rwanda ishami rya Rukara\nbaje ku rubyiniro nabo bunga mu rya bagenzi babo, barabyina bajya mu\nkinimba,mu mishyayayo... maze inama nkemurampaka yari ikuriwe na\nMariya Yohana akazi kayibana akazi</div>\n&nbsp;\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/a0fQVBL.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/x1quAnr.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\">ABAGIZE INAMA NKEMURAMPAKA</div>\n<div align=\"left\">\n\n\nNyuma yuko amatorero uko ari atatu amaze kurushanwa inkera yakomeje\nmaze bahamagara ku rubyiniro kabuhariwe Munyakazi Deo inanga\narayikirigita karahava.\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1N9bOPw.jpg\" width=\"543\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\">MUNYAKAZI DEO\n\nNyuma inama nkemurampaka yaje gutangaza ko indahigwa za IPRC ya Kigali\narizo zihize andi matorero maze umudiho n\'ikobe by\'indahigwa biba\nbyose bishimira intsinzi.</div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dD951Zp.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\">BATANGAZA UWATSINZE\n\nNyuma inkera y\'inyamibwa yaje gusozwa n\'Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier mu\nbisigo n\'imivugo biherejejwe n\'umurya w\'inanga wa Munyakazi Deo ndetse\nn\'iningiri ya Bageni Hyacinte</div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2GmAVg7.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\">UMUSIZI TUYISENGE\nNdabibutsa ko mu nkera y\'inyamibwa ari naho hamurikiwe urubuga rwa\ninternet <a href=\"http://wwww.rcpi.rw/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://wwww.rcpi.rw&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1505031444201000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFEa7uoyT4UjIraqQaRy-wnRDROdA\">wwww.rcpi.rw</a> ruzajya rufasha guhuza abanyeshuri ndetse\nnabandi bantu bashaka guteza imbere umuco nyarwanda nk\'intego yarwo\nnkuko twabitangarijwe na Mutarasisi Uwayo Christian umuyobozi wa\nRwanda Culture Promoters Initiative.</div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9ynuwC8.jpg\" width=\"360\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\">CHRISTIAN MUTARASISI UWAYO UMUYOBOZI WA RCPI</div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\">ANDI MAFOTO:</div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RbVEnDt.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tEAscTV.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\">aba M.C MUNEZERO na UWIMANA</div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WpD5KZe.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FWatzKi.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n&nbsp;\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GtdSDze.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>', 'Inkera y\'inyamibwa Itorero Indahigwa rya IPRC ya Kigali ryahize andi matorero ya za kaminuza /AMAFOTO', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '49-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-12-03 16:34:36', '2017-12-03 16:34:36', '', 49, 'http://new.umucowacu.com/2017/12/03/49-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
