(452, 2, '2017-12-03 16:50:41', '2017-12-03 16:50:41', '<b>Igitaramo inkera y\'inyamibwa ni amarushanwa azahuriza hamwe amatorero ndangamuco ya za kaminuza 4 hano mu Rwanda,iki gitaramo kikazaba ku wa gatanu tariki ya 8 Nzeri 2017 muri Kigali Serena Hotel.</b>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Inkera y\'inyamibwa ni amarushanwa ari gutegurwa na Rwanda Culture\r\nPromoters Initiative umuryango w\'abanyeshuri b\'abanyarwanda bari muri\r\nza Kaminuza  zitandukanye hano mu Rwanda ndetse no mu bindi bihugu 14\r\nbitandukanye byo ku isi bagamije guteza imbere umuco nyarwanda.\r\n\r\nMu kiganiro kirambuye ikinyamakuru Umucowacu.com cyagiranye na Bwana\r\nMutarasisi Uwayo christian uhagarariye Rwanda Culture Promoters\r\nInitiative yatangiye atubwira byinshi kuri iyi nkera y\'inyamibwa no ku\r\nmuryango yashinze muri rusange agira ati &lt;&lt;Rwanda Culture Promoters Initiate twiyemeje guteza imbere umuco nyarwanda cyane cyane mu rubyiruko kuko ugenda ucika, hanyuma aya marushanwa turi gutegura y\'inkera y\'inyamibwa afite udushya twinshi,ikindi kandi icyiza nuko ku munyeshuri ufite ikarita y\'ishuri kwinjira ari ubuntu.&gt;&gt;\r\n\r\nMudarasisi yakomeje atangariza ikinyamakuru umuco wacu ko inkera y\'inyamibwa izitabirwa n\'amatorero ndangamuco ane ahagarariye za kaminuza enye, ayo matorero ni Itorero rya kaminuza y\'u Rwanda(UR), Itorero rya kaminuza ya Mount Kenya,Itorero rya kaminuza ya UTB(yahoze ari RTUC) ndetse n\'itorero rya kaminuza ya IPRC Kigali.\r\n\r\nMu gitaramo inkera y\'inyamibwa uretse kandi aya matorero azarushanwa,hazanagaragaramo ibikorwa bindi byerekana umuco, nk\'imyiyereko y\'abahanzi berekana bakanahimba imyambaro ishingiye ku muco nyarwanda.\r\nIki gitaramo kandi kizasusurutswa na Wimas Band mu rwego rwo kwibutsa abazakitabira uburyohe mw\'umuziki nyarwanda wo hambere.\r\n\r\nMu gitaramo inkera y\'inyamibwa hazanamurikwa urubuga nkoranyambaga(websites) ruzajya ruhuza abanyarwanda bose bakunda umuco wabo baba abimbere mu gihugu cyangwa hanze yacyo(Diaspora) mu rwego rwo kungurana ibitekerezo ku iterambere ry\'umuco nyarwanda.</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/K98cXDA.jpg\" width=\"615\" height=\"436\" /></div>\r\n<div align=\"left\">\r\nNdabibutsa ko inkera y\'inyamibwa izaba kuri uyu wa gatanu tariki ya 8\r\nNzeri 2017 guhera i saa kumi n\'imwe z\'umugoroba muri Kigali Serena Hotel kwinjira ni 2000Rwf ahasanzwe ndetse na 5000Rwf mu cyubahiro ku munyeshuri ufite ikarita y\'ishuri\r\nkwinjira ni ubuntu. Gucikwa ni ukunyagwa zigahera.</div>', 'Amatorero ndangamuco yaza Kaminuza zitandukanye hano mu Rwanda agiye guhurira mu marushanwa yiswe \"Inkera y\'Inyamibwa\".', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '53-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-03 16:50:41', '2017-12-03 16:50:41', '', 53, 'http://new.umucowacu.com/2017/12/03/53-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(453, 2, '2017-12-03 17:05:02', '2017-12-03 17:05:02', '<b>Poetic fever ni igitaramo cy\'ubusizi cyabaye ku mugoroba wo kuri uyu gatandatu tariki ya 16 Nzeri i Kigali muri Blue Note.</b>\n<div align=\"left\">Transpoesis yari isanzwe imenyerewe mu gutegura amarushanwa nayo y\'ubusizi yiswe Kigali Vibrates with Poetry amarushanwa ngaruka gihembwe. Kuri ubu Transpoesis igiye kujya ifatanya ibyo bikorwa\nbyombi ari amarushanwa ndetse ni iki gitaramo poetic fever kizajya kiba ngarukakwezi nkuko twabitangarijwe na Dr Andrea Grieder umuyobozi wa Transpoesis.</div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZYIKTEY.jpg\" width=\"515\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\">\nPoetic Fever ni igitaramo cyatangiye ahagana ku i saa mbili z\'umugoroba mu mujyi wa Kigali rwagati mu Kabari kitwa Blue Note,maze ku ikubitiro Kivumbi cyangwa Lion King abimburira abandi basizi\nbinyura imbaga mu gisigo cye kiri mu rurimi rw\'icyongereza yise\" King meet</div>\n<div align=\"left\">  king\",igitaramo cyaje gukomeza maze abasizi bagiye batandukanye barimo Bahati Innocent, Ella Bikwemu,Delice Mukazi,Carine Maniraguha,Andrea Grieder,Amina Umuhoza, Esther Uwibambe basusurutsa abitabiriye poetic fever karahava.\nNyuma y\' igitaramo ikinyamakuru umuco wacu cyaganiriye numwe mu basizi\nbitabiriye iki gitaramo ari we Kivumbi(Lion King) atangaza uko\nyiyumva. Yatangiye agira ati&lt;&lt; Ku nshuro ya mbere nishimiye ubwitabire bw\'abantu muri iki gitaramo ikindi ndashimira cyane Dr Andrea Grieder\nkubw\'uru rubuga yashyiriyeho abasizi Imana imuhe umugisha,ndagira ngo kandi mbwire abakunda ubusizi ko bashonje bahishiwe kuko ibikorwa byo ni byinshi&gt;&gt;.</div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ATqqPOp.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\">\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4aDDypI.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div align=\"left\">\nDr Andrea Grieder</div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/f9GaDCQ.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\">\nIki gitaramo kikaba cyari gifite umwihariko wuko buri musizi wese\nyacurangirwaga ibisigo bye abifashijwemo na Band yitwa Kinga Blues\nihagarariwe n\'umunyamuziki ukomoka mu gihugu cy\'Uburundi Arnauld\nNganji.</div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><b> REBA AMAFOTO</b>:</div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Kw5hC8s.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\n\n\n\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MHXZpwE.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/91gjU4z.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zlbFPXo.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9zWMpSn.jpg\" width=\"424\" />\n\n\n\n\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VPLujVX.jpg\" width=\"499\" />\n\n\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SFalW9I.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\">\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6SD3pUa.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q1jwn1d.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0OxzOdA.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\">\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eZgM219.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/P96IGZu.jpg\" width=\"395\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cUvJKxZ.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OlawOhC.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/77LsBYj.jpg\" width=\"540\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yVRf0GB.jpg\" width=\"540\" /></div>\n<div align=\"left\">\nntagihindutse igitaramo \"<b>Poetic Fever</b>\" kizongera kuba ku\nwa 14 Ukwakira uyu mwaka nubundi muri Blue Note.</div>', 'Transpoesis yamaze gukora ikindi gitaramo cy\'ubusizi yise \'\'Poetic Fever\'\'.AMAFOTO', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11