"0\" />\r\nByari ibyishimo ku baturage bo mu Karere ka Nyanza n\'abifatanyije nabo  <img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/36033650103_86959b58ca_k-79ef2.jpg?1503856317\" width=\"326\" height=\"218\" border=\"0\" /> <img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/36842593855_8fc88b23cb_k-418de.jpg?1503856317\" width=\"296\" height=\"198\" border=\"0\" /> <img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/intore_z_urukerereza_zavunnye_sambwe_benshi_baranyurwa-15a15.jpg?1503856317\" width=\"225\" height=\"150\" border=\"0\" />\r\nIntore z\'Urukerereza zavunnye sambwe, benshi baranyurwa  <img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/umuganura_3-f1155.jpg?1503865179\" width=\"243\" height=\"163\" border=\"0\" /> <img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH756/umuganura_4-9dcfb.jpg?1503865180\" width=\"238\" height=\"181\" border=\"0\" /> <img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/rutangarwamaboko_modeste_nzayisenga_n_umugore_we_umuziranenge_sana_cynthia-58728.jpg?1503865180\" width=\"255\" height=\"170\" border=\"0\" /> <img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/umuganura_1-0d074.jpg?1503865180\" width=\"293\" height=\"196\" border=\"0\" /> <img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/36033677593_8bc455c378_k-75434.jpg?1503856316\" width=\"337\" height=\"225\" border=\"0\" /> <img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH812/umuganura_17-241e2.jpg?1503865180\" width=\"358\" height=\"291\" border=\"0\" /> <img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/umuganura_19-bccf8.jpg?1503865180\" width=\"415\" height=\"277\" border=\"0\" /> <img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/36672082362_a68adec6a2_k-e657c.jpg?1503856317\" width=\"361\" height=\"241\" border=\"0\" /> <img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/ama_g_the_black_mu_bahanzi_baririmbye-47084.jpg?1503856317\" width=\"383\" height=\