(485, 2, '2017-12-04 08:26:29', '2017-12-04 08:26:29', '<b>Kuwa 19 Nyakanga 2017 ubwo Perezida Kagame yajyaga kwiyamamariza mu karere ka Bugesera yari yaherekejwe n\'abanyarwanda batari bake barimo na Miss Iradukunda Elsa,</b>\r\n<div align=\"left\">\r\n\r\n AMATEKA YA Iradukunda Elsa ni umukobwa muremure w’inzobe ushinguye, ukunda guseka akagira amenyo yererana mu ishinya nziza y’umukara,niwe Nyampinga w’u Rwanda umwaka wa 2017.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col col-lg-12\" align=\"left\">\r\n<div class=\"fulltext margintop10\">\r\n\r\nYabyawe na Samuel Mana ufite ibiro by’ivunjisha mu Mujyi wa Kigali rwagati naho nyina akitwa Mukandekezi Christine akora akazi k’ubucuruzi, batuye mu Kagari ka Kanserege, mu Murenge wa Gikondo, mu Karere ka Kicukiro.\r\n\r\nIradukunda Elsa areshya na metero imwe na sentimetero 76 (1,76cm) akaba apima ibiro 50. Afite imyaka 19 y’amavuko kuko yavutse kuwa 25 Werurwe 1998, avuka mu muryango w’abana umunani[abakobwa batandatu n’abahungu babiri] akaba ari uwa kane.\r\n\r\nMu ijoro rya taliki 25 Gashyantare 2017 Iradukunda Elsa yatorewe kuba Nyampinga uhiga abandi mu buranga n’ubuhanga. Yahawe ibihembo bikomeye birimo imodoka nziza ya Suzuki SX4 ifite agaciro ka miliyoni 15 z’amafaranga y’u Rwanda.\r\n\r\nMu gihe cy’umwaka azamarana ikamba azajya ahembwa umushahara w’amafaranga ibihumbi magana inani (800,000frw) bivuze ko ku mwaka azajya aba yahawe miliyoni icyenda n’ibihumbi Magana atandatu (9,600,000Rwf) hakiyongeraho n’ibindi bihembo bitandukanye.\r\n\r\nAzahabwa ibindi bihembo birimo imyambaro igezweho, gukorerwa imisatsi buri kwezi, kogerezwa imodoka, gutemberezwa mu mahanga ya kure ndetse mu mpera z’umwaka wa 2017 azaserukira u Rwanda mu irushanwa ry’ubwiza rya Miss World.\r\n\r\nIradukunda Elsa avuga adategwa indimi eshatu, Igifaransa, Icyongereza n’Ikinyarwanda. Yari ahagarariye Intara y’u Burengerazuba, .\r\n\r\nUmushinga yifuza gukora mu gihe azamarana ikamba rya Nyampinga w’u Rwanda ngo ‘ni ugufasha leta guha ingufu gahunda ya Made in Rwanda’ no guteza imbere ba rwiyemezamarimo bafite ibikorwa byihariye bishyigikira umurongo arimo.\r\n\r\nKuwa 19 Nyakanga 2017 ubwo Perezida Kagame yajyaga kwiyamamariza mu karere ka Bugesera yari yaherekejwe n\'abanyarwanda batari bake barimo na Miss Iradukunda Elsa, uyu ukunze kugaragara aherekeza Perezida Kagame ahantu hanyuranye aba yagiye kwiyamamaza, icyakora mu mafoto yafotowe uyu mukobwa biragaragara ko yagize amahirwe yo guhura imbonankubone na Perezida Kagame ndetse n’umufasha we.\r\n<div><b>REBA MU MAFOTO UKO BYARI BIMEZE:</b>\r\n<div class=\"artlogo\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201707/logos/1500537794_logo.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img class=\" b-error\" src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201707/logos/1500537794_logo.jpg\" alt=\"Miss Iradukunda Elsa yagize amahirwe yo guhura imbonankubone na Perezida Kagame –AMAFOTO\" /></a></div>\r\n<strong><em><img class=\" b-loaded\" src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201707/attachments/1500542497_4.jpg\" alt=\"miss rwanda\" />Iradukunda Elsa aganira na Perezida Kagame</em></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><em><img class=\" b-loaded\" src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201707/attachments/1500542497_3.jpg\" alt=\"miss rwanda\" />Miss Elsa Iradukunda yaganiriye kandi na Madame Jeannette Kagame</em></strong>\r\n\r\nTukimara kubona aya mafoto twifuje kumenya uko uyu mukobwa yakiriye guhura n’umuryango wa Perezida Kagame, adutangariza ko yabyishimiye cyane. Miss Elsa Iradukunda yabwiye umucowacu.com  ko i cyari cyiraje inshinga ari ugushyigikira  uwasubije agaciro umunyarwandakazi ndetse akamuha  ijambo kandi njyewe ndi urugero rwiza  rwuko twahawe ijambo.\r\n\r\n<strong><em><img class=\" b-loaded\" src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201707/attachments/1500542497_2.jpg\" alt=\"miss rwanda\" /><img class=\" b-loaded\" src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201707/attachments/1500542498_1.jpg\" alt=\"miss rwanda\" width=\"1080\" height=\"708\" />Miss Rwanda Iradukunda Elsa ari mu rubyiruko rwanahuye na muzehe Ngarambe François umunyamabanga mukuru wa FPR-Inkotanyi</em></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Tumubajije  ubutumwa yatanga muri icyigihe cy\'amatora ati:Inama nagira  abanyarwanda nugutora umucandida  babona ubereye U Rwanda uwo babona uzabageza ku Rwanda  </em></strong><em><b>bifuza.</b></em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'IKIGANIRO na Miss Iradukunda Elsa Nyuma yo kugaragara ari kumwe na Perezida Kagame yatanze ubutumwa – REBA AMAFOTO', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '154-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-04 08:26:29', '2017-12-04 08:26:29', '', 154, 'http://new.umucowacu.com/2017/12/04/154-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
