(545, 2, '2017-12-13 09:26:03', '2017-12-13 09:26:03', 'Mu rwego rwo kwimakaza umuco wo gutarama no guhiga nk’imwe mu nzira zo kugaruka ku isoko y’umurage w’u Rwanda no kuwuhesha agaciro , Itorero Indahigwa za IPRC gihugu ryateguye igitaramo cyiswe “Indahigwa Twataramye”.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/GRN9165-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />\r\n\r\nAbagize Indahigwa bateguye igitaramo cy’inkera  kizabera kuri IPRC ya Kigali -Kicukiro  ku itariki ya 15 Ukuboza 2017  guhera saa kumi nebyri nigice z’umugoroba.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_548\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/GRN9192-300x167.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"167\" /> Indahigwa[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIndahigwa  ni itorero ndangamuco rya IPRC ryashinzwe mu mwaka wa 2015\r\n\r\nNDAHIRIWE Emmy umuyobozi wa Indahigwa , yabwiye umucowacu.com ,“Iki gitaramo cy’Inkera y’Abahizi gihishiye abazacyitabira kubasubiza ku muzi w’umuco wo gutarama no guhiga mu Rwanda. Imbyino, Imihamirizo, umurishyo w’ingoma, n’indirimbo byose biherekejwe n’ibicurangisho gakondo bizumvikanisha urwunge rw’amajwi y’indashyikirwa,”.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_549\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/IMG-20171212-WA0012-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /> Umuyozi w\'Indahigwa[/caption]\r\n\r\nakomeza atubwira ko Intego yigitaramo ari \"<strong>Uruhare rw\'urubyiruko mugusigasira umuco nyarwanda\"</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/GRN9177-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />\r\n\r\nIndahigwa  ni abasore n\'inkumi 45 biyemeje kwimakaza umuco\r\n\r\nIgitaramo kizabera kuri IPRC ku itariki ya 15 Ukuboza 2017  guhera saa kumi nebyri nigice z’umugoroba, kwinjira  ni ubuntu\r\n\r\nIndahigwa za IPRC niryo torero ryahize andi yaza kaminuza  riza kumwanya  wa mbere muri uyu mwaka .\r\n\r\nUwashaka  Indahigwa yazisanga kuri IPRC Kigali aho zitaramira buri wese ndetse nushaka ko ibirori bye bisusuruka  niho yabasanga\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_552\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Indahigwa-Twataramye1-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /> Urupapuro rwamamaza igitaramo[/caption]\r\n\r\nAbandi bazaba muri ikigitaramo harimo Umusore w\'umunyarwanda <em>Deo Munyakazi</em>, uzobereye mu gucuranga inanga nyarwanda,ukunzwe cyane nabatari bakeya\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Copy-of-DSC_7282-300x199.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nMunyakazi Deo azaba akirigita inanga\r\n<h6>UMVA HANO:Isoko Dusangiye ya Deo Munyakazi</h6>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m1SwVtruaz8\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m1SwVtruaz8</a>\r\n\r\nMuri ikigitaramo kandi hazaba harimo Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier nawe ukunzwe cyane nabenshi.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/IMG-20170708-WA0007-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<h6>UMVA HANO:Niba ari Ibyo nta Rwanda ya  Tuyisenge Olivier</h6>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uaMkjwV8Ayo\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uaMkjwV8Ayo</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nItorero Indahigwa  ryashinzwe mu mwaka wa 2015, rifite inshingano yo guteza imbere umurage gakondo w’u Rwanda mu mbyino n’indirimbo gakondo.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://umucowacu.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Indahigwa-Twataramye1-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIgitaramo kizabera kuri IPRC ku itariki ya 15 Ukuboza 2017  guhera saa kumi nebyri nigice z’umugoroba, kwinjira  ni ubuntu', 'Itorero Indahigwa za IPRC kigali  zateguye igitaramo \'Indahigwa Twataramye\'', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'itorero-indahigwa-za-iprc-kigali-zateguye-igitaramo-indahigwa-twataramye', '', '', '2017-12-13 10:50:06', 