(576, 2, '2017-12-13 21:25:58', '2017-12-13 21:25:58', '<p>Abakobwa bifuza guhatanira ikamba rya Nyampinga w’u Rwanda 2018 baratangira kwiyandikisha mu ijoro ryo kuri uyu wa Gatatu, rikaba ari irushanwa ririmo impinduka mu mitegurire, abazaryitabira n’aho rizabera.</p><p>Itorwa rya Miss Rwanda ryateguwe na Mashirika muri 2012, na ho kuva mu mwaka wa 2014 isoko ryatsindiwe na Rwanda Inspiration Backup ku bufatanye n’abaterankunga baryo ku isonga hari Cogebanque, ari na bo batangiye igikorwa cyo gushaka Nyampinga 2018 uzasimbura Iradukunda Elsa.</p><p>Nk’uko Ishimwe uyobora Rwanda Inspiration Backup yabitangaje mu kiganiro n’itangazamakuru cyabaye kuri uyu wa Gatatu tariki 13 Ukuboza 2017, kuva saa sita z’ijoro, abakobwa bifuza guhatanira ikamba rya Nyampinga w’u Rwanda, baratangira kwiyandikisha banyuze ku rubuga rwa ‘Miss Rwanda’.</p><p>Ibikorwa by’ijonjora bizatangira tariki 13 Mutarama 2018 mu Karere ka Musanze, tariki 14 Mutarama 2018 bikomereze mu Karere ka Rubavu, ku ya 20 Mutarama 2018 ni mu Karere ka Huye, tariki 21 Mutarama 2018 bikomereze mu Karere ka Kayonza bikazasorezwa mu Mujyi wa Kigali tariki 27 Mutarama 2018.</p><p>Ishimwe yatangaje ko uyu mwaka Miss Rwanda izagaragaramo impinduka zitandukanye zirimo ko mu majonjora hazatoranywa abakobwa 30 aho kuba 25 nk’uko byari bisanzwe nyuma hakazakorwa irindi jonjora rizasigazamo abakobwa 20. Aba nibo bazerekeza mu mwiherero aho kuba 15 bari basanzwe bajyamo.</p><p>Yagize ati “Izi ni impinduka zigamije kudufasha kubona Miss Rwanda iva ku rwego rumwe ikajya ku rundi. No mu mwiherero hazakorwa bya bikorwa basanzwe bakora birimo kwiga umuco, kumenya igihugu cyabo ariko noneho hazajya hakorwa n’ikizamini mbere y’uko umuntu agera ku munsi wa nyuma w’irushanwa.”</p><p>Yakomeje agira ati “Ni ikizamini cyanditse aho umuntu azabazwa ibibazo bisanzwe hakanababo ikiganiro [interview] aho buri mukobwa azajya abazwa n’akanama nkemurampaka ku buryo yifuza ko umushinga we wafasha Abanyarwanda. Hazabaho gutora kuri sms ndetse harebwe n’imyitwarire y’umukobwa, uko abana n’abandi, umuco n’indangagaciro.”</p><p>Izindi mpinduka ziri mu irushanwa rya 2018 ni uko umubare w’ibisonga bya Nyampinga wavuye kuri bine hakazatoranywa bibiri gusa.</p><p>Ishimwe yavuze ko bitewe n’uko buri mukobwa yasaga n’ukora umushinga we ku giti cye, noneho bazatoranya imishinga itatu bakayikorera hamwe bikaba ari yo mpamvu umubare w’ibisonga wagabanutse.</p><p><strong><em><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201712/attachments/1513169455__dsc0710.jpg\" alt=\"Miss Rwanda 2018\" /> </em></strong></p><p>Ibirori byo gutora Miss Rwanda byakuwe mu ihema rya Camp Kigali kuri iyi nshuro bikazabera muri Kigali Convention Center ndetse n’amasaha bimara akaba yaragabanyijwe, atazongera kurenga abiri n’igice.</p><p><strong>Ibisabwa kugira ngo umukobwa yiyandikishirize guhatanira ikamba rya Miss Rwanda 2018:</strong></p><p><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L8xH11/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\" alt=\"-\" width=\"8\" height=\"11\" /> Kuba ari Umunyarwandakazi</p><p><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L8xH11/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\" alt=\"-\" width=\"8\" height=\"11\" /> Kuba afite hagati y’imyaka 18-24</p><p><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L8xH11/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\" alt=\"-\" width=\"8\" height=\"11\" /> Kuba yararangije amashuri yisumbuye</p><p><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L8xH11/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\" alt=\"-\" width=\"8\" height=\"11\" /> Kuba avuga neza Ikinyarwanda n’urundi rurimi, hagati y’Icyongereza, Igifaransa n’Igiswahili</p><p><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L8xH11/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\" alt=\"-\" width=\"8\" height=\"11\" /> Kuba afite indeshyo ya sentimetero 170 kuzamura</p><p><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L8xH11/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\" alt=\"-\" width=\"8\" height=\"11\" /> Kuba apima ibiro hagati ya 45-70</p><p><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L8xH11/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\" alt=\"-\" width=\"8\" height=\"11\" /> Kuba atari yabyara</p><p><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L8xH11/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\" alt=\"-\" width=\"8\" height=\"11\" /> Kuba yiteguye kumara nibura umwaka atuye mu Rwanda, igihe yatsinze</p><p><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L8xH11/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\" alt=\"-\" width=\"8\" height=\"11\" /> Kuba atiteguye gukora ubukwe mu gihe cy’umwaka yambaye ikamba</p><p><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L8xH11/puce-32883.gif?1498415905\" alt=\"-\" width=\"8\" height=\"11\" /> Kuba yiteguye guhagararira u Rwanda mu gihe bikenewe</p><p>Mu bihembo Nyampinga azahabwa harimo imodoka nshya ya Suzuki n’umushahara w’ibihumbi 800 by’amafaranga y’u Rwanda bizatangwa na Cogebanque, amatike y’indege azatangwa na RwandAir, kumwishyurira salon akoreshamo imisatsi umwaka, kumwambika igihe cyose agiye mu marushanwa, kumwishyurira internet y’umwaka n’ibindi.</p><p><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201712/attachments/1513169454__dsc0696.jpg\" alt=\"Miss Rwanda 2018\" width=\"810\" height=\"542\" /></p><p><strong><em><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201712/attachments/1513169455__dsc0710.jpg\" alt=\"Miss Rwanda 2018\" /></em></strong></p><p><strong><em>Miss Iradukunda n\'abategura Miss Rwanda ubwo bari imbere y\'abanyamakuru</em></strong></p><p><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; width: 640px; display: block; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" title=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.touchrwanda.com/wp-content/up